# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-07-09 15:26

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:6
translate spanish d10a_b15ef64b:

    # Z "Fangs. Is there any news on the Hive?"
    Z "Fangs. ¿Hay alguna noticia sobre la Colmena?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:8
translate spanish d10a_ba09ca8f:

    # Z "Maybe it's time we go back, now that the girl has had time to reconnect with her mother?"
    Z "¿Quizá sea el momento de volver, ahora que la chica ha tenido tiempo de reencontrarse con su madre?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:11
translate spanish d10a_1789e1aa:

    # Fa "If we knew anything, we'd be able to make a decision, for sure."
    Fa "Si supiéramos algo, podríamos tomar una decisión, seguro."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:12
translate spanish d10a_2719f35b:

    # Fa "But we don't know anything more than when we left the place."
    Fa "Pero no sabemos nada más que cuando dejamos el lugar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:15
translate spanish d10a_a9f6fb0b:

    # Fa "And after it went so horribly wrong the last time, I'm not sure if it's at all worth it."
    Fa "Y después de que saliera tan horriblemente mal la última vez, no estoy seguro de que merezca la pena."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:16
translate spanish d10a_8dc49d8f:

    # Fa "After what they did to Keen and Towser, I can't risk sending yet another group there."
    Fa "Después de lo que les hicieron a Keen y Towser, no puedo arriesgarme a enviar otro grupo allí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:19
translate spanish d10a_2680999e:

    # Z "You want to abandon the mission and have their deaths mean nothing?"
    Z "¿Quieres abandonar la misión y que sus muertes no signifiquen nada?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:22
translate spanish d10a_0c7431b3:

    # Fa "No, that's not what I meant. But we can't send in another squad and risk losing more of our people."
    Fa "No, no me refería a eso. Pero no podemos enviar otro escuadrón y arriesgarnos a perder a más de los nuestros."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:25
translate spanish d10a_5bcd019a:

    # Fa "I was thinking to go in there myself, actually."
    Fa "De hecho, estaba pensando en ir yo misma."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:26
translate spanish d10a_9ee8ac26:

    # Fa "I got us into this mess, so if I can get in there and check out the place again, just me, I'd sneak in and out with less risk for everybody."
    Fa "Yo nos metí en este lío, así que, si entro sola a revisar el lugar de nuevo, podré entrar y salir con menos riesgo para todos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:29
translate spanish d10a_2f0f7b9e:

    # Fa "If anything should happen, I can move quicker than a full squad could."
    Fa "Si ocurre algo, puedo moverme más rápido de lo que podría hacerlo un escuadrón completo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:32
translate spanish d10a_d9bfd7d3:

    # Fa "...and if these bastards get me too, they {i}only{/i} get me."
    Fa "... y si estos cabrones me pillan a mí también, {i}sólo{/i} me pillan a mí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:35
translate spanish d10a_d94be69a:

    # Z "You're the one who holds this place together. You can't go."
    Z "Eres la que mantiene este lugar unido. No puedes irte."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:36
translate spanish d10a_fbffe3df:

    # Z "I will do it. Give me one of your vehicles, and I will check the place out again."
    Z "Yo lo haré. Dame uno de tus vehículos y volveré a revisar el lugar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:39
translate spanish d10a_222e19db:

    # Fa "...?"
    Fa "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:40
translate spanish d10a_6c820c3a:

    # Z "I've been dealing with situations like these for years."
    Z "Llevo años lidiando con situaciones como ésta."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:41
translate spanish d10a_55189bb9:

    # Z "I know what I'm doing, and we can't really wait all too long."
    Z "Sé lo que estoy haciendo y no podemos esperar demasiado."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:42
translate spanish d10a_b74be945:

    # Z "Think of it; what if that girl wasn't accepted back by her mother and we left her there to die?"
    Z "Piénsalo; ¿qué pasaría si esa chica no fuera aceptada de nuevo por su madre y la dejáramos allí para que muriera?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:45
translate spanish d10a_7924b173:

    # Fa "I am not happy sending anyone, other than myself, in there on a solo mission. I'd rather engage our full forces, than losing someone else."
    Fa "No me gusta enviar a nadie, aparte de mí, en una misión en solitario. Prefiero comprometer a todas nuestras fuerzas, que perder a alguien más."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:48
translate spanish d10a_0cf2bc2d:

    # Z "How about this instead: send just me in there, and give me Pepper for backup, in case I or anyone else needs patching up."
    Z "¿Qué te parece esto? Envíame solo a mí y dame a Pepper como apoyo, por si yo o alguien más necesita atención médica."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:49
translate spanish d10a_bb318454:

    # Z "She can wait outside, hidden in safety, until things are safe in there."
    Z "Ella puede esperar fuera, escondida a salvo, hasta que las cosas estén seguras allí dentro."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:50
translate spanish d10a_7a5166c1:

    # Z "What do you say?"
    Z "¿Qué dices?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:53
translate spanish d10a_3cf7bfdd:

    # Fa "Fuck no! She's our main and best scientist. I'm not sending her in the field again, not after what happened last time."
    Fa "¡Ni de coña! Es nuestra principal y mejor científica. No voy a enviarla de nuevo al campo, no después de lo que pasó la última vez."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:56
translate spanish d10a_ad47992f:

    # Z "Yes, she's an expert on mutants and humans alike, right?"
    Z "Sí, es una experta en mutantes y humanos, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:59
translate spanish d10a_73ff97fc:

    # Fa "She's invaluable."
    Fa "Tiene un valor incalculable."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:62
translate spanish d10a_3da5ffd1:

    # Z "I agree, but... do you know anybody else who you would trust the health of a mutant to?"
    Z "Estoy de acuerdo, pero... ¿conoces a alguien más a quien confiarías la salud de un mutante?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:65
translate spanish d10a_d3226b83:

    # Fa "What does this have to do with anything?"
    Fa "¿Qué tiene que ver eso con todo esto?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:68
translate spanish d10a_d872c211:

    # Z "The Queen. If Ivy's arrows have wounded her seriously, do you trust anybody other than Pepper to be able to save her?"
    Z "La Reina. Si las flechas de Ivy la han herido gravemente, ¿confías en que alguien más que Pepper pueda salvarla?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:69
translate spanish d10a_49445ef2:

    # Z "We can't afford another fuck up. If our, my, survival depends on our ability to patch up the Queen and be of any assistance to them, Pepper is our best chance."
    Z "No podemos permitirnos otra cagada. Si nuestra, mi, supervivencia depende de nuestra capacidad para curar a la Reina y serles de ayuda, Pepper es nuestra mejor oportunidad."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:72
translate spanish d10a_ee5cf3aa:

    # Fa "{i}*Sigh*{/i}...Okay then. You have a point, all things considered."
    Fa "{i}*suspiro*{/i}... De acuerdo. Visto así, tienes razón."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:73
translate spanish d10a_c2b67e64:

    # Fa "Even so, she is precious to me, to us... our group. I will not put her in danger if she does not come willingly."
    Fa "Aun así, ella es preciosa para mí, para nosotros... nuestro grupo. No la pondré en peligro si ella no viene de buen grado."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:76
translate spanish d10a_41cb90e5:

    # Fa "Go and talk to her, see what she says, and take one of the buggies if you head out."
    Fa "Ve a hablar con ella, a ver qué te dice, y coge uno de los buggies si sales."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:79
translate spanish d10a_56b84288:

    # Fa "And please, be careful out there. I don't want to lose you, Pepper or anyone else for this."
    Fa "Y por favor, ten cuidado ahí fuera. No quiero perderte a ti, a Pepper ni a nadie más por esto."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:82
translate spanish d10a_92c3e642:

    # Z "I don't know why, but I have a feeling that leaving the girl behind, allowing her to reconnect, must have had a positive impact."
    Z "No sé por qué, pero tengo la sensación de que dejar a la chica atrás, permitiéndole volver a conectar, debe haber tenido un impacto positivo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:83
translate spanish d10a_d183c3d6:

    # Z "It's what her mother wanted in the first place, after all. That should give us some credit with her."
    Z "Después de todo, eso es lo que su madre quería desde el principio. Debería hacernos ganar algunos puntos con ella."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:84
translate spanish d10a_55e1729c:

    # Z "We will be back before you know it."
    Z "Volveremos antes de que te des cuenta."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:87
translate spanish d10a_9b727321:

    # "You depart towards Pepper's laboratory..."
    "Te diriges hacia el laboratorio de Pepper..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:91
translate spanish d10a_fd4b54b1:

    # Z "How is the girl doing? Is she alright?"
    Z "¿Cómo está la chica? ¿Está bien?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:94
translate spanish d10a_aaca8195:

    # Fa "She's doing good. She's adapting well."
    Fa "Está bien. Se está adaptando bien."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:95
translate spanish d10a_c88b677d:

    # Fa "I would even go as far as saying she's rapidly becoming one of us."
    Fa "Incluso me atrevería a decir que se está convirtiendo rápidamente en una de nosotros."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:98
translate spanish d10a_1f2b39c2:

    # Fa "She still has some of the Hive mannerisms left in her, but she's doing better, if slowly."
    Fa "Todavía conserva algunos gestos propios de la Colmena, pero va mejorando, aunque poco a poco."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:101
translate spanish d10a_4c9127c3:

    # Z "So what's her new name then? Did you decide?"
    Z "Entonces, ¿cuál es su nuevo nombre? ¿Lo has decidido?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:104
translate spanish d10a_ff6cbf42:

    # Fa "You know, she's quite tall, and her eyes still go wide when she's nervous."
    Fa "Sabes que es bastante alta, y sus ojos se abren mucho cuando está nerviosa."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:105
translate spanish d10a_1b76f1b4:

    # Fa "So we call her Mantis. Red came up with her name."
    Fa "Así que la llamamos Mantis. A Red se le ocurrió su nombre."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:106
translate spanish d10a_158555e0:

    # Fa "Some of the other girls are still freaked out about her, given recent events, but they're trying to hide it."
    Fa "Algunas de las otras chicas aún están asustadas por ella, dados los recientes acontecimientos, pero intentan disimularlo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:109
translate spanish d10a_22efbf16:

    # Z "So what do we do about her mother?"
    Z "¿Y qué hacemos con su madre?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:112
translate spanish d10a_3b522a4d:

    # Fa "Ivy shot her twice, and even if she's still alive, I don't think she's going to think better of us after what happened last time around."
    Fa "Ivy le ha disparado dos veces, y aunque siga viva, no creo que piense bien de nosotros después de lo que pasó la última vez."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:113
translate spanish d10a_1f09c71b:

    # Fa "I can't risk losing more of us to this, and I don't see how any one of us can convince the Hive to join our cause now."
    Fa "No puedo arriesgarme a perder a más de nosotros por esto, y no veo cómo ninguno de nosotros puede convencer a la Colmena de que se una a nuestra causa ahora."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:116
translate spanish d10a_548c5276:

    # Fa "Maybe you should ask the girl herself about it. It's her mother that's still in there, after all."
    Fa "Tal vez debas preguntarle a la propia chica al respecto. Al fin y al cabo, es su madre la que sigue ahí dentro."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:119
translate spanish d10a_7aa09704:

    # Z "Good point. What if she's in favour of going there again? Will you join us?"
    Z "Buena observación. ¿Y si ella quiere volver allí? ¿Te unirás a nosotros?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:122
translate spanish d10a_ac48c7a8:

    # Fa "Last time we went in there with a full squad, and it didn't go well."
    Fa "La última vez fuimos allí con una escuadra completa, y no nos fue bien."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:123
translate spanish d10a_901077cf:

    # Fa "We can't risk losing control again. I would send in three people, at most."
    Fa "No podemos arriesgarnos a perder el control de nuevo. Yo enviaría a tres personas, como máximo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:124
translate spanish d10a_f2a5f5ff:

    # Fa "Considering the mother may still be wounded, we need Pepper there. She is our best healer, medic, she says."
    Fa "Teniendo en cuenta que la madre puede estar todavía herida, necesitamos a Pepper allí. Ella es nuestra mejor sanadora, médico, dice."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:127
translate spanish d10a_29378c26:

    # Fa "So either you or me, should take Mantis back there, with Pepper staying out of sight, ready to come in as soon as we know that it's safe."
    Fa "Así que tú o yo, deberíamos llevar a Mantis de vuelta allí, con Pepper permaneciendo fuera de la vista, lista para entrar tan pronto como sepamos que es seguro."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:130
translate spanish d10a_65521bac:

    # Z "You are what keeps this place together, so it should be me. I will go. I've dealt with all kinds of weird situations before."
    Z "Tú eres quien mantiene este lugar unido, así que debería ir yo. Iré. Ya he lidiado antes con todo tipo de situaciones extrañas."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:133
translate spanish d10a_7ead974b:

    # Fa "Fine, but please, be careful. I don't want to lose another soldier to that hive bitch."
    Fa "De acuerdo, pero por favor, ten cuidado. No quiero perder a otro soldado por esa zorra de la colmena."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:134
translate spanish d10a_883b58d3:

    # Fa "If there's any sign of danger, pull out immediately. This mission has already been enough of a disaster."
    Fa "Si hay alguna señal de peligro, retírate inmediatamente. Esta misión ya ha sido suficientemente desastrosa."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:137
translate spanish d10a_a7d03a40:

    # Z "Let us see what your new soldier thinks of all this first."
    Z "Veamos qué piensa tu nueva soldado de todo esto primero."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:138
translate spanish d10a_93844717:

    # Z "See you later, Fangs."
    Z "Hasta luego, Fangs."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:141
translate spanish d10a_1a94c0d3:

    # "You get up and head towards the training room..."
    "Te levantas y te diriges hacia la sala de entrenamiento..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:147
translate spanish d10a6_82486b1c:

    # Re "Try faster, decisive strikes."
    Re "Intenta golpes más rápidos y decisivos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:148
translate spanish d10a6_a9d8cbf2:

    # Re "You want to strike them, not push them away."
    Re "Quieres golpearlos, no alejarlos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:151
translate spanish d10a6_12f61775:

    # Mant "..."
    Mant "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:152
translate spanish d10a6_43fca45c:

    # Re "Hey, you look troubled. Is everything okay?"
    Re "Oye, pareces preocupada. ¿Va todo bien?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:155
translate spanish d10a6_ff428e67:

    # Re "You can take a break if you want."
    Re "Puedes tomarte un descanso si quieres."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:158
translate spanish d10a6_aff35521:

    # Re "Not like we're in a rush here, you know."
    Re "No es que tengamos prisa, ¿sabes?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:161
translate spanish d10a6_12f61775_1:

    # Mant "..."
    Mant "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:168
translate spanish d10a6_62b54b60:

    # Z "Ladies, I need to speak with Mantis for a second."
    Z "Señoras, necesito hablar un momento con Mantis."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:171
translate spanish d10a6_eda8a86b:

    # Re "Hey [persistent.player_name]. That's your name, right?"
    Re "Oye, [persistent.player_name]. Ese es tu nombre, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:174
translate spanish d10a6_7919ea31:

    # Re "We were just training a bit, but she doesn't seem into it today."
    Re "Estábamos entrenando un poco, pero hoy no parece estar interesada."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:175
translate spanish d10a6_53c20bb2:

    # Re "So go ahead, what did you need to discuss?"
    Re "Entonces, adelante, ¿de qué teníais que hablar?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:178
translate spanish d10a6_bfd12b80:

    # Z "I was speaking to Fangs about what happened."
    Z "Estuve hablando con Fangs sobre lo ocurrido."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:179
translate spanish d10a6_29bdc9c1:

    # Z "And I was wondering if you are ready to find out what became of your mother."
    Z "Y me preguntaba si estás preparada para saber qué ha sido de tu madre."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:180
translate spanish d10a6_822638ca:

    # Z "She seemed to care for you, before everything escalated."
    Z "Parecía que se preocupaba por ti, antes de que todo se intensificara."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:183
translate spanish d10a6_1247d461:

    # Mant "Mother never cared for us, [persistent.player_name]. Mother always cared about the Hive, but then, the Hive is us."
    Mant "Madre nunca se preocupó por nosotros, [persistent.player_name]. Madre siempre se preocupó por la Colmena, pero entonces, la Colmena somos nosotros."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:186
translate spanish d10a6_7e48b109:

    # Mant "You must understand. We are no longer connected to the Hive."
    Mant "Debes entenderlo. Ya no estamos conectados a la Colmena."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:187
translate spanish d10a6_eecf8fa8:

    # Mant "We..."
    Mant "Nosotros..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:190
translate spanish d10a6_029ea8db:

    # Mant "I..."
    Mant "Yo..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:193
translate spanish d10a6_e7daee0d:

    # Mant "I... have a new family now. This is my home, [persistent.player_name]."
    Mant "Yo... tengo una nueva familia ahora. Este es mi hogar, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:198
translate spanish d10a6_ffc0067a:

    # Re "She has changed since you convinced her to turn a new leaf, [persistent.player_name]."
    Re "Ha cambiado desde que la convenciste de pasar página, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:199
translate spanish d10a6_2185df9f:

    # Re "Getting used to her... quirks, isn't simple, but Fangs told us to accept her, and in her own way, her differences make her one of us, so here we are."
    Re "Acostumbrarse a sus... peculiaridades, no es sencillo, pero Fangs nos dijo que la aceptáramos, y a su manera, sus diferencias la convierten en una de nosotras, así que aquí estamos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:202
translate spanish d10a6_c6638f96:

    # Re "And as you can see, she's adapting quite well. I've grown to like her even."
    Re "Y como puedes ver, se está adaptando bastante bien. Incluso ha llegado a gustarme."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:207
translate spanish d10a6_1a0ed9e9:

    # Z "I'm glad it's all working out for her."
    Z "Me alegro de que todo le vaya bien."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:210
translate spanish d10a6_38795879:

    # Re "It's good to see her more hap-"
    Re "Es bueno verla más fel..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:213
translate spanish d10a6_370cf1cd:

    # Mant "It is not over yet."
    Mant "Todavía no se ha acabado."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:214
translate spanish d10a6_3a772ee6:

    # Mant "Towser and Keen died because they wanted to speak to Mother about working with the Hive."
    Mant "Towser y Keen murieron porque querían hablar con Madre sobre el trabajo con la Colmena."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:215
translate spanish d10a6_2dd84c77:

    # Mant "Isn't that why you took me back with you?"
    Mant "¿No es por eso por lo que me llevaste contigo?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:220
translate spanish d10a6_fe4e9913:

    # Z "I took you back because I did not want you to come to harm in the fight."
    Z "Te traje de vuelta porque no quería que sufrieras daño durante la lucha."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:221
translate spanish d10a6_2223fcf9:

    # Z "You escaped your mother once. I was afraid she might hurt you, or worse."
    Z "Una vez escapaste de tu madre. Temía que te hiciera daño, o algo peor."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:224
translate spanish d10a6_12f61775_2:

    # Mant "..."
    Mant "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:225
translate spanish d10a6_c8dd578b:

    # Z "I'm sorry you had to go through this."
    Z "Siento que hayas tenido que pasar por esto."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:228
translate spanish d10a6_03f8fd4b:

    # Mant "Perspectives change, [persistent.player_name]."
    Mant "Las perspectivas cambian, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:229
translate spanish d10a6_f447ca69:

    # Mant "Before Fangs took me in, the only thing that mattered was the Hive."
    Mant "Antes de que Fangs me acogiera, lo único que importaba era la Colmena."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:230
translate spanish d10a6_15b75bb2:

    # Mant "And now..."
    Mant "Y ahora..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:233
translate spanish d10a6_e08c5319:

    # Mant "But we must go again, or else my new companions died for nothing."
    Mant "Pero debemos volver a ir, o mis nuevos compañeros habrán muerto en vano."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:234
translate spanish d10a6_dcb40902:

    # Mant "If mother is still alive, she might listen to me."
    Mant "Si madre sigue viva, puede que me escuche."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:237
translate spanish d10a6_9ad83a50:

    # Z "Then we must speak to Pepper. If your mother is still alive, she is wounded."
    Z "Entonces debemos hablar con Pepper. Si tu madre sigue viva, está herida."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:238
translate spanish d10a6_d947f413:

    # Z "Are you ready to go?"
    Z "¿Estás preparada para ir?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:241
translate spanish d10a6_9aec8804:

    # Mant "Yes. We want to fix this... I do."
    Mant "Sí. Queremos arreglar esto...  Lo haré."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:245
translate spanish d10a6_afa923f2:

    # Z "You're one of Fangs' people now."
    Z "Ahora eres una de las de Fangs."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:246
translate spanish d10a6_272da1bb:

    # Z "I would hope that you can convince your mother that you are happy here and convince her to work with us."
    Z "Espero que puedas convencer a tu madre de que eres feliz aquí, y convencerla de que trabaje con nosotros."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:247
translate spanish d10a6_0149947b:

    # Z "That is why I took you in."
    Z "Por eso te he acogido."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:250
translate spanish d10a6_3e3b1578:

    # Mant "We... no... I am happy here, indeed. This is my new home."
    Mant "Nosotros... no...  Yo soy feliz aquí, de verdad. Este es mi nuevo hogar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:253
translate spanish d10a6_aa47aa39:

    # Mant "But Mother, she will not see it that way."
    Mant "Pero madre, ella no lo verá así."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:254
translate spanish d10a6_23b08256:

    # Mant "The Hive is always connected. But I am not part of it anymore. I do not know what to think."
    Mant "La Colmena siempre está conectada. Pero yo ya no formo parte de ella. No sé qué pensar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:255
translate spanish d10a6_948cbda7:

    # Mant "We must go there, [persistent.player_name]. Because we... I need to at least try to get her on our side. If the Hive has not turned on her..."
    Mant "Debemos ir allí, [persistent.player_name]. Porque nosotros...  Tengo que intentar al menos ponerla de nuestro lado. Si la Colmena no se ha vuelto contra ella..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:256
translate spanish d10a6_ef8d54d5:

    # Z "I didn't know they could."
    Z "No sabía que podían hacerlo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:257
translate spanish d10a6_c12874c3:

    # Mant "They can not. Not without causing their own destruction, but they don't know that."
    Mant "No pueden. No sin causar su propia destrucción; pero ellos no lo saben."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:260
translate spanish d10a6_08106779:

    # Z "Then we must speak to Pepper. If your Mother is still alive, she will need her help."
    Z "Entonces debemos hablar con Pepper. Si tu madre sigue viva, necesitará su ayuda."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:261
translate spanish d10a6_d947f413_1:

    # Z "Are you ready to go?"
    Z "¿Estás preparada para ir?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:264
translate spanish d10a6_dfe8c4ad:

    # Mant "Yes. Let us go, please."
    Mant "Sí. Vayamos, por favor."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:268
translate spanish d10a6_21ec1b22:

    # Z "But what about our mission? To get the hive to work with us?"
    Z "¿Pero qué pasa con nuestra misión? ¿Conseguir que la colmena trabaje con nosotros?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:271
translate spanish d10a6_e85796c8:

    # Re "Well, I-"
    Re "Bueno, yo-"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:274
translate spanish d10a6_510f612b:

    # Mant "You are right, [persistent.player_name]. Keen and Towser gave their lives for this. That should mean something."
    Mant "Tienes razón, [persistent.player_name]. Keen y Towser dieron su vida por esto. Eso debería significar algo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:277
translate spanish d10a6_a2839ac0:

    # Mant "But...We are lost. We... I... am no longer part of the Hive."
    Mant "Pero... Estamos perdidos. Nosotros...  Yo... ya no soy parte de la Colmena."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:278
translate spanish d10a6_09590a48:

    # Mant "...but I need to know if mother is still alive. She did not want this to happen."
    Mant "... pero necesito saber si mamá sigue viva. Ella no quería que esto sucediera."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:281
translate spanish d10a6_92f99393:

    # Z "Then we must speak to Pepper. If your mother is still alive, she will need help."
    Z "Entonces debemos hablar con Pepper. Si tu madre sigue viva, necesitará ayuda."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:282
translate spanish d10a6_d947f413_2:

    # Z "Are you ready to go?"
    Z "¿Estás preparada para ir?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:285
translate spanish d10a6_d0d66e6d:

    # Mant "Let us finish what we started... what I started."
    Mant "Terminemos lo que hemos empezado... lo que yo he empezado."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:291
translate spanish d10a27_9aa2d0b3:

    # "Soon after..."
    "Poco después..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:294
translate spanish d10a27_3e2d5a10:

    # Pe "Suicide. That's what this sounds like."
    Pe "Un suicidio. Eso es lo que parece."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:297
translate spanish d10a27_547a1ef0:

    # Pe "Don't get me wrong Mantis, if Fangs trusts you, so do I."
    Pe "No me malinterpretes Mantis, si Fangs confía en ti, yo también."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:298
translate spanish d10a27_ed800079:

    # Pe "But you still need to give me a reason to go into a place that clearly is hostile to us - for a second time."
    Pe "Pero todavía tienes que darme una razón para entrar en un lugar que es claramente hostil para nosotros, por segunda vez."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:301
translate spanish d10a27_3f40e046:

    # Pe "The odds of this being a course of action that does not result in catastrophic failure are astronomically small."
    Pe "Las probabilidades de que este curso de acción no provoque un fracaso catastrófico son astronómicamente pequeñas."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:304
translate spanish d10a27_e07f88c7:

    # Mant "Last time we... and I was scared. I did not expect what the Hive has become."
    Mant "En la última ocasión... me asusté. No me esperaba en lo que se ha convertido la Colmena."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:305
translate spanish d10a27_1f61a17a:

    # Mant "Now I know what might happen. I am ready to face Mother."
    Mant "Ahora sé lo que puede pasar. Estoy preparada para enfrentarme a Madre."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:306
translate spanish d10a27_8b111829:

    # Mant "If anything goes bad, you run, and leave me behind."
    Mant "Si algo va mal, corres y me dejas atrás."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:307
translate spanish d10a27_297054c1:

    # Z "It won't come to this."
    Z "No llegaremos a eso."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:308
translate spanish d10a27_c8fe6ad1:

    # Z "Pepper, we should at least take a look at the building from the outside."
    Z "Pepper, al menos deberíamos echar un vistazo al edificio desde fuera."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:309
translate spanish d10a27_510e05e9:

    # Z "The Hive did not follow us outside, the last time."
    Z "La Colmena no nos siguió fuera, la última vez."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:310
translate spanish d10a27_bba9370f:

    # Z "Maybe they're under control now, maybe they're starved at this point."
    Z "Tal vez ahora esté bajo control, o tal vez esté hambrienta en este momento."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:311
translate spanish d10a27_4cffa7b4:

    # Z "All we need you to do is hang back and only show yourself in case someone needs medical attention."
    Z "Lo único que necesitamos es que te quedes atrás y sólo te muestres en caso de que alguien necesite atención médica."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:312
translate spanish d10a27_04db5759:

    # Z "Can you do that?"
    Z "¿Podrás hacerlo?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:315
translate spanish d10a27_c6722a9c:

    # Pe "I could. Although I am still not fully convinced, considering we lost two of our soldiers already."
    Pe "Podría. Aunque todavía no estoy completamente convencida, considerando que ya hemos perdido dos de nuestros soldados."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:318
translate spanish d10a27_938a8e54:

    # Pe "So, who's going? Fangs, you, Mantis, me... who else?"
    Pe "Entonces, ¿quién va? Fangs, tú, Mantis, yo... ¿quién más?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:321
translate spanish d10a27_94e8fedf:

    # Z "Fangs is not coming with us. We agreed on a small squad of three."
    Z "Fangs no viene con nosotros. Acordamos un pequeño escuadrón de tres."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:322
translate spanish d10a27_59ad307d:

    # Z "You, Mantis and me. That's all."
    Z "Tú, Mantis y yo. Eso es todo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:323
translate spanish d10a27_fe885dbf:

    # Z "Do you want to debate the logic, the odds and the statistical improbabilities on this choice as well, or are you up for the job?"
    Z "¿Quieres debatir también la lógica, las probabilidades y las improbabilidades estadísticas de esta elección, o estás dispuesta a hacerlo?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:324
translate spanish d10a27_e2212afe:

    # Pe "Hm."
    Pe "Umm."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:327
translate spanish d10a27_7d7793ef:

    # Pe "{i}*sigh* Fine."
    Pe "{i}*suspiro* Está bien."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:330
translate spanish d10a27_a7f2a89b:

    # Pe "Let's get it right this time, shall we."
    Pe "Hagamos las cosas bien esta vez, ¿de acuerdo?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:331
translate spanish d10a27_f210812c:

    # Pe "Go ahead and get the car started, I'll meet you there."
    Pe "Ve a poner en marcha el coche, nos encontraremos allí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:335
translate spanish d10a27_ff22a89b:

    # "As you eventually arrive in the area, it becomes immediately clear that something has changed from the last time you visited."
    "Cuando llegas a la zona, queda inmediatamente claro que algo ha cambiado desde la última vez que la visitaste."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:336
translate spanish d10a27_2820b1dd:

    # "Screams can be heard from every corner of the cathedral-like building's surroundings."
    "Se oyen gritos desde todos los rincones de los alrededores del edificio con aspecto de catedral"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:337
translate spanish d10a27_d463c718:

    # "The same bloodcurdling screeches that accompanied your previous confrontation."
    "los mismos chillidos espeluznantes que acompañaron tu anterior enfrentamiento."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:338
translate spanish d10a27_8aa4b812:

    # "It seems as though the Hive brutes are scattered all around, skulking in whatever shadows they can find."
    "Parece que los brutos de la Colmena están dispersos por todas partes, acechando en cualquier sombra que puedan encontrar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:339
translate spanish d10a27_cf5e0cf8:

    # "Knowing this, you keep Pepper close to you, to avoid any kind of surprise attack."
    "Sabiendo esto, mantienes a Pepper cerca de ti, para evitar cualquier tipo de ataque sorpresa."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:340
translate spanish d10a27_1021e941:

    # "Together, you carefully head inside, ready to fall back at any moment..."
    "Juntos, os dirigís cuidadosamente hacia el interior, preparados para retroceder en cualquier momento..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:346
translate spanish d10a27_810dfba1:

    # Z "That's still her..."
    Z "Eso es todavía su..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:347
translate spanish d10a27_600f26be:

    # Mant "We... she is resting, wounded."
    Mant "Nosotros... ella está descansando, herida."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:348
translate spanish d10a27_253f46c3:

    # Pe "You think it's safe in here?"
    Pe "¿Crees que es seguro aquí?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:349
translate spanish d10a27_215e9ac4:

    # Mant "The Hive is scared, hungry. It is scattered."
    Mant "La Colmena está asustada, hambrienta. Está dispersa."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:350
translate spanish d10a27_b04500be:

    # Mant "I can hear... some are still around."
    Mant "Puedo oír... que algunos aún están por aquí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:353
translate spanish d10a27_28a4dda2:

    # Mant "Mother has lost control... but we don't need to fear an attack."
    Mant "Madre ha perdido el control... pero no debemos temer un ataque."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:354
translate spanish d10a27_002daa4f:

    # Mant "We can heal her wounds."
    Mant "Podemos curar sus heridas."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:357
translate spanish d10a27_dabf9917:

    # Pe "Are you sure we should? Maybe she can't be trusted."
    Pe "¿Estás segura de que debemos hacerlo? Quizá no se pueda confiar en ella."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:360
translate spanish d10a27_17e13128:

    # Mant "We can not, want not, let Mother die."
    Mant "No podemos, no queremos, dejar morir a Madre."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:363
translate spanish d10a27_b311dc89:

    # Mant "Mother did not attack us. The Hive was hungry."
    Mant "Madre no nos atacó. La Colmena tenía hambre."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:366
translate spanish d10a27_0ac15407:

    # Z "Pepper, stay behind us and prepare to break out."
    Z "Pepper, quédate detrás de nosotros y prepárate para salir."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:367
translate spanish d10a27_6dec8430:

    # Z "Let's head to the mother step by step."
    Z "Dirijámonos a madre paso a paso."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:370
translate spanish d10a27_7de09f47:

    # Mant "I will go first, [persistent.player_name]."
    Mant "Yo iré primero, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:373
translate spanish d10a27_d09eee2f:

    # "As you make your approach, the immediate surroundings seem quiet and peaceful enough."
    "Al acercarte, el entorno inmediato parece bastante tranquilo y pacífico."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:376
translate spanish d10a27_12f61775:

    # Mant "..."
    Mant "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:377
translate spanish d10a27_6a4c9553:

    # Pe "This is honestly... unexpected."
    Pe "Esto es sinceramente... inesperado."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:378
translate spanish d10a27_c9dc6199:

    # Pe "She doesn't seem to be in critical condition."
    Pe "Ella no parece estar en estado crítico."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:381
translate spanish d10a27_7c0644ee:

    # Pe "The arrows didn't hit vital areas, and the flesh around it has... healed?"
    Pe "Las flechas no alcanzaron zonas vitales, y la carne que la rodea se ha... ¿curado?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:382
translate spanish d10a27_5f3c1ce6:

    # Pe "I wonder if she could move, if she wanted."
    Pe "Me pregunto si podría moverse, si quisiera."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:385
translate spanish d10a27_bb686b4f:

    # Mant "So mother is not... hurt. We suspected this could be so."
    Mant "Así que madre no está... herida. Sospechábamos que podía ser así."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:386
translate spanish d10a27_036786b0:

    # Mant "I mean... I thought so."
    Mant "Es decir... Me lo imaginaba."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:389
translate spanish d10a27_f541dee7:

    # Mant "The Hive regenerates. But she is still weak."
    Mant "La Colmena se regenera. Pero ella sigue estando débil."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:392
translate spanish d10a27_764c44aa:

    # Mant "Mother... hear my voice. I have come."
    Mant "Madre... escucha mi voz. He venido."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:395
translate spanish d10a27_7d1866a4:

    # HQ "..."
    HQ "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:398
translate spanish d10a27_ea413124:

    # Z "Hey, I think I heard something from upstairs."
    Z "Oye, creo que he oído algo arriba."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:399
translate spanish d10a27_083e927c:

    # Z "Mind if I check it out for a second?"
    Z "¿Te importa si lo compruebo un momento?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:402
translate spanish d10a27_7a5e5086:

    # Mant "Are you sure you want to, [persistent.player_name]?"
    Mant "¿Estás seguro de que quieres hacerlo, [persistent.player_name]?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:403
translate spanish d10a27_8df9403a:

    # Mant "The Hive consumes. You may not want to see what you find."
    Mant "La Colmena consume. Puede que no quieras ver lo que encuentras."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:412
translate spanish d10a27_f2d4df46:

    # Z "I need to take a look. I will be back soon."
    Z "Necesito echar un vistazo. Yo volveré enseguida."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:415
translate spanish d10a27_3921facc:

    # "You head up the stairs..."
    "Subes las escaleras..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:421
translate spanish d10a27_608f93c7:

    # Zt "This place is dark..."
    Zt "Este lugar es oscuro..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:424
translate spanish d10a27_e0031752:

    # Zt "That's the floor... those noises..."
    Zt "Ese es el suelo... esos ruidos..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:427
translate spanish d10a27_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:428
translate spanish d10a27_78fdc4c8:

    # Zt "Is that... Keen?"
    Zt "Es eso...  ¿Keen?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:432
translate spanish d10a27_8945326d:

    # Mu "{i}*guzzling noises*"
    Mu "{i}*ruidos de engullimiento*"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:435
translate spanish d10a27_6b005fbf:

    # "Even knowing that Keen and Towser had not survived, the scene that played out in front of you still left you disturbed."
    "Incluso sabiendo que Keen y Towser no habían sobrevivido, la escena que se desarrolló ante ti te dejó perturbado."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:436
translate spanish d10a27_af049b0e:

    # "Keen's eyes were gouged out, her limbs were torn off her body, and her clothes were stripped off her body and torn to shreds."
    "A Keen le arrancaron los ojos, le arrancaron las extremidades y y sus ropas fueron despojadas de su cuerpo y hechas pedazos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:437
translate spanish d10a27_8ec61bff:

    # "You can only hope that the pain she endured did not last for too long..."
    "Sólo puedes esperar que el dolor que soportó no durara demasiado tiempo..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:440
translate spanish d10a27_c2b6a85e:

    # "Towser's body was decapitated and barely recognizable. At least he found a quick end..."
    "El cuerpo de Towser estaba decapitado y apenas reconocible. Al menos tuvo un rápido final..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:443
translate spanish d10a27_623946d7:

    # "After witnessing that gruesome spectacle, you decide to head back..."
    "Después de presenciar ese espantoso espectáculo, decides regresar..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:452
translate spanish d10a63_1d0d6991:

    # Pe "That should do."
    Pe "Con esto bastará."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:453
translate spanish d10a63_fa6eb9fc:

    # Pe "If her body really regenerates this quickly, she should be fine anyway, but a few stitches will at least speed the healing process up."
    Pe "Si su cuerpo realmente se regenera tan rápido, ella debería estar bien, pero en cualquier caso, unos puntos de sutura al menos acelerarán el proceso de curación."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:454
translate spanish d10a63_6f95c31f:

    # Mant "Thank you, Pepper."
    Mant "Gracias, Pepper."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:457
translate spanish d10a63_0eed0d5c:

    # HQ "You..."
    HQ "Tú..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:458
translate spanish d10a63_ef8887fb:

    # Mant "Mother?"
    Mant "¿Madre?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:459
translate spanish d10a63_dd2998f9:

    # HQ "You said... your... voice."
    HQ "Has dicho... tu... voz."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:462
translate spanish d10a63_d69fa0b9:

    # HQ "Why have you come here, daughter... to humiliate us?"
    HQ "¿Por qué has venido aquí, hija... a humillarnos?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:463
translate spanish d10a63_d81708b0:

    # HQ "You... have changed. We don't... recognise you..."
    HQ "Tú... has cambiado. No... te reconocemos..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:466
translate spanish d10a63_32de56cd:

    # Mant "Mother, these people can help us. Get us out of this place!"
    Mant "Madre, esta gente puede ayudarnos. Sácanos de este lugar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:469
translate spanish d10a63_62792fcb:

    # Mant "No more darkness. The Hive makes us blind to the outside, and blind to ourselves. I have seen what's out there."
    Mant "No más oscuridad. La Colmena nos ciega ante el exterior y ante nosotros mismos. He visto lo que hay ahí fuera."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:470
translate spanish d10a63_82f4c751:

    # Mant "We don't need to hide anymore. We can do better than this. Please, come with me... join us."
    Mant "No necesitamos escondernos más. Podemos hacerlo mejor que esto. Por favor, ven conmigo... únete a nosotros."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:471
translate spanish d10a63_14ea62c5:

    # Mant "I can show you that they're good for us!"
    Mant "Puedo demostrarte que son buenos para nosotros."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:474
translate spanish d10a63_81ed0a7a:

    # HQ "Don't tell us what we should do!"
    HQ "¡No nos digas lo que debemos hacer!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:477
translate spanish d10a63_53315f1c:

    # HQ "You have left the Hive. You have left us. You are no longer seeing what we see."
    HQ "Has dejado la Colmena. Nos has dejado a nosotros. Ya no ves lo que nosotros vemos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:478
translate spanish d10a63_6b62b1ad:

    # HQ "We have lost our daughter... and what is this thing that comes back?"
    HQ "Hemos perdido a nuestra hija... ¿y qué es esto que regresa?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:479
translate spanish d10a63_226cd4d5:

    # HQ "To look at us, as we starve?!"
    HQ "¡¿Para mirarnos, mientras nos morimos de hambre?!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:482
translate spanish d10a63_8ecf3254:

    # Mant "I came back to convince you... that there are other ways."
    Mant "He vuelto para convencerte... de que hay otros caminos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:485
translate spanish d10a63_4b06a5f8:

    # Pe "If... I am not mistaken, Fangs mentioned something about a trade of some sort."
    Pe "Si...  no me equivoco, Fangs mencionó algo sobre un intercambio de algún tipo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:488
translate spanish d10a63_e9aa4d12:

    # Z "She is right. We were thinking of offering food in return for your mother's help."
    Z "Ella tiene razón. Estábamos pensando en ofrecer comida a cambio de la ayuda de tu madre."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:491
translate spanish d10a63_6eec3a2b:

    # Pe "Did she also mention what that food source is?"
    Pe "¿Mencionó también cuál es esa fuente de alimento?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:492
translate spanish d10a63_580cfbfe:

    # Pe "If I recall, she mentioned giving our prisoners of war to the Hive."
    Pe "Si no recuerdo mal, ella mencionó de dar nuestros prisioneros de guerra a la Colmena."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:493
translate spanish d10a63_b4e0aeac:

    # Pe "Are you sure that's what we want?"
    Pe "¿Estás seguro de que eso es lo que queremos?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:496
translate spanish d10a63_afa9bd4c:

    # Z "I don't think we need to discuss that right now."
    Z "No creo que tengamos que discutir eso ahora mismo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:497
translate spanish d10a63_d21117a5:

    # Z "The way I see it, some of us have already made up their minds..."
    Z "Tal y como yo lo veo, algunas ya se han decidido..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:501
translate spanish d10a63_12f61775:

