translate spanish d10b_7609f835:

    # Zt "So... let's see..."
    Zt "Así que... veamos..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1629
translate spanish d10b_72d33687:

    # Zt "A settlement directly between old Cairo and the barren lands."
    Zt "Un asentamiento directamente entre el Viejo Cairo y las tierras áridas."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1630
translate spanish d10b_4719b7d6:

    # Zt "...the \"best\" of two worlds, great..."
    Zt "... lo \"mejor\" de dos mundos, genial..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1634
translate spanish d10b_0310aacc:

    # "You step into your car and head out into the desert."
    "Subes a tu coche y te diriges al desierto."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1635
translate spanish d10b_ac9c7cdb:

    # "After a good while, the sky slowly changes its colours."
    "Después de un buen rato, el cielo cambia lentamente de color."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1636
translate spanish d10b_1f13f902:

    # "It's late into the afternoon, when you finally see the remains of the highway the Queen mentioned."
    "Ya es tarde, cuando por fin ves los restos de la carretera que mencionó la Reina."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1637
translate spanish d10b_7d42d644:

    # "To your surprise, the settlement is not built near or around the highway, but actually on top of it."
    "Para tu sorpresa, el asentamiento no está construido cerca o alrededor de la carretera, sino encima de ella."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1638
translate spanish d10b_82d90f89:

    # "A weird smell hangs in the air as you make your way towards it, dodging concrete rubble and the remains of ancient constructions..."
    "Un extraño olor flota en el aire mientras te abres paso, esquivando escombros de hormigón y restos de antiguas construcciones..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1641
translate spanish d10b_488bf961:

    # Zt "Solid steel ramps to fix the gaps..."
    Zt "Rampas sólidas de acero para arreglar los huecos..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1642
translate spanish d10b_c48ae4d6:

    # Zt "I'm impressed. That must've taken an effort to get them out here."
    Zt "Estoy impresionado. Debe haber supuesto un esfuerzo para traerlas aquí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1645
translate spanish d10b_5907d5c1:

    # "You slowly drive your car over them..."
    "Pasas lentamente por encima de ellas..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1646
translate spanish d10b_98e5b8d8:

    # Zt "Let's hope they hold..."
    Zt "Esperemos que aguanten..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1649
translate spanish d10b_cf940086:

    # "You keep driving. As you draw closer, you hear someone shouting..."
    "Sigues conduciendo. A medida que te acercas, oyes que alguien grita..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1652
translate spanish d10b_feaee1a9:

    # SG "Alright man, that's far enough. Nice and slowly now..."
    SG "Muy bien, tío, ya está bien. Despacio y con calma..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1653
translate spanish d10b_0b6c7b22:

    # SG "Bring her in front of the gate."
    SG "Llévalo delante de la puerta."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1656
translate spanish d10b_5a646f2a:

    # SG "Good, now pause, turn the engine off and get out... slowly."
    SG "Bien, ahora haz una paradita, apaga el motor y sal... despacio."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1659
translate spanish d10b_ffb42ed7:

    # SG "We need to know who the fuck we're dealing with here."
    SG "Necesitamos saber con quién cojones estamos tratando."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1668
translate spanish d10b_86e991b3:

    # SG "Good. Now, you don't exactly look like one of these wastelanders that come here for work."
    SG "Bien. Ahora, no pareces exactamente uno de esos baldíos que vienen aquí a trabajar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1671
translate spanish d10b_089af0ab:

    # SG "So what the hell brings you here?"
    SG "Así que... ¿qué demonios te trae por aquí?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1672
translate spanish d10b_b571337e:

    # SG "You one of those Stalkers or some shit?! Fancy ride you got there for sure."
    SG "¿Eres uno de esos Acechadores o algo así? Seguro que has tenido un bonito paseo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1677
translate spanish d10b_f094e88a:

    # Z "I am. I'm here on behalf of the Queen of Zeta."
    Z "Así es. Estoy aquí en nombre de la Reina de Zeta"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1678
translate spanish d10b_0ce63ab2:

    # Z "So whoever is in charge here... I need to speak to him."
    Z "Así que quienquiera que esté al mando aquí...  Necesito hablar con él."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1681
translate spanish d10b_0577c23a:

    # SG "A guest from high places, huh..."
    SG "Un invitado de las altas esferas, eh..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1684
translate spanish d10b_85e67741:

    # SG "We will let you through."
    SG "Te dejaremos pasar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1685
translate spanish d10b_89204804:

    # SG "You can park your car on the left side, behind the gate."
    SG "Puedes aparcar tu coche en el lado izquierdo, detrás de la verja."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1686
translate spanish d10b_ccc47585:

    # SG "And don't worry, the workers won't come near it."
    SG "Y no te preocupes, los trabajadores no se acercarán a ella."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1689
translate spanish d10b_7abc3de6:

    # SG "Sef! Open the gate!"
    SG "¡Sef! ¡Abre la puerta!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1693
translate spanish d10b_30f197d7:

    # Z "You're speaking to one indeed. I need to see your boss."
    Z "Estás hablando con uno de ellos. Necesito ver a tu jefe."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1696
translate spanish d10b_76634506:

    # SG "Interesting. But I'm not sure why he would need to speak to you."
    SG "Interesante. Pero no estoy seguro de por qué necesitaría hablar contigo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1697
translate spanish d10b_e4fdc8ed:

    # SG "But I'll leave that call to him. Better make it worth his time..."
    SG "Pero le dejaré esa decisión a él. Mejor que merezca la pena su tiempo..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1700
translate spanish d10b_7abc3de6_1:

    # SG "Sef! Open the gate!"
    SG "¡Sef! ¡Abre la puerta!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1705
translate spanish d10b_87f81c7e:

    # Z "Isn't it a bit warm to wear a gas mask?!"
    Z "¿No hace un poco de calor para llevar una máscara antigás?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1706
translate spanish d10b_d47eb120:

    # Z "Or is that part of the dress code around here, because I am not seeing any storms."
    Z "O eso forma parte del código de vestimenta de aquí, porque no veo ninguna tormenta."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1707
translate spanish d10b_bbbd5ffa:

    # SG "..."
    SG "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1710
translate spanish d10b_1d81ffef:

    # SG2 "These fucking Zetans..."
    SG2 "Estos malditos zetanos..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1713
translate spanish d10b_50dda02e:

    # SG2 "Hey, asshole. You know damn well why some people have to wear these things. Acting like you've never seen that..."
    SG2 "Oye, gilipollas. Sabes muy bien por qué algunas personas tienen que llevar estas cosas. Actúas como si nunca hubieras visto algo así..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1714
translate spanish d10b_50b02264:

    # SG2 "So leave her alone, alright?!"
    SG2 "Así que olvídate de ella, ¿de acuerdo?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1717
translate spanish d10b_05c96562:

    # SG "It's okay Sef, I got this."
    SG "Está bien Sef, yo me encargo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1720
translate spanish d10b_136c8a41:

    # SG "Listen dude, I have no time for this."
    SG "Escucha, amigo, no tengo tiempo para esto."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1721
translate spanish d10b_7758f219:

    # SG "Answer the question. You must be one of those Stalkers. So why are you here?"
    SG "Responde a la pregunta. Debes de ser uno de esos Acechadores. ¿Y por qué estás aquí?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1726
translate spanish d10b_05573a02:

    # Z "I'm here on behalf of the Queen of Zeta."
    Z "Estoy aquí en nombre de la Reina de Zeta."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1727
translate spanish d10b_8c34dbae:

    # Z "So whoever is in charge around here... I need to speak to them."
    Z "Así que quien quiera que esté al mando por aquí...  Tengo que hablar con ellos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1730
translate spanish d10b_0577c23a_1:

    # SG "A guest from high places, huh..."
    SG "Un invitado de las altas esferas, eh..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1733
translate spanish d10b_c6658a40:

    # SG "Fine, we will let you through. You can park your car on the left side behind the gate."
    SG "Bien, te dejaremos pasar. Puedes aparcar tu coche en el lado izquierdo, detrás de la puerta."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1736
translate spanish d10b_c4b4fcb1:

    # SG "Sef! Open up!"
    SG "¡Sef! ¡Abre la puerta!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1737
translate spanish d10b_3dfea3fc:

    # SG2 "Fine... but if it was up to me, he'd be turning around."
    SG2 "Bien... pero si fuera por mí, se daría la vuelta."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1738
translate spanish d10b_7d6ba9f2:

    # SG2 "Arrogant Zetans..."
    SG2 "Zetanos arrogantes..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1742
translate spanish d10b_30f197d7_1:

    # Z "You're speaking to one indeed. I need to see your boss."
    Z "Estás hablando con uno de ellos. Necesito ver a tu jefe."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1745
translate spanish d10b_791b4bf2:

    # SG "And why do you think he wants to speak to a Stalker?"
    SG "¿Y por qué crees que quiere hablar con un Acechador?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1746
translate spanish d10b_f3adc337:

    # SG "But sure, go ahead, speak to him. That's going to be fun to watch."
    SG "Pero claro, adelante, habla con él. Será divertido verlo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1749
translate spanish d10b_c45b8483:

    # SG "You better have something important to say, and good luck to you if you don't..."
    SG "Más vale que tengas algo importante que decir, y buena suerte si no lo tienes..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1752
translate spanish d10b_fd12c05d:

    # SG "Sef, you can open the gate."
    SG "Sef, puedes abrir la puerta."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1753
translate spanish d10b_43b90cf7:

    # SG2 "Fine, fine..."
    SG2 "Bien, bien..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1761
translate spanish d10b17_6ed10d28:

    # SG2 "Fine... if it was up to me, he'd be turning around."
    SG2 "Bien... si de mí dependiera, se daría la vuelta."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1762
translate spanish d10b17_e5d58164:

    # SG "Go past the workers and talk to the tower guard ahead, he will let you through."
    SG "Pasa por delante de los trabajadores y habla con el guardia de la torre, te dejará pasar"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1763
translate spanish d10b17_636875af:

    # SG "Enjoy your stay... I guess. I hope you brought your own water."
    SG "Disfruta de tu estancia...  supongo. Espero que hayas traído tu propia agua."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1766
translate spanish d10b17_945178cd:

    # "You park your vehicle inside, as suggested..."
    "Aparcas tu vehículo en el interior, como te han sugerido..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1769
translate spanish d10b17_37104da3:

    # "As you enter the settlement, you hear old rusty windmills creaking through the wind."
    "Al entrar en el asentamiento, oyes viejos molinos de viento oxidados que crujen con el viento."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1770
translate spanish d10b17_f71ce6ee:

    # "The air is dry, the sun is warm, but not as stinging as back in the desert."
    "El aire es seco, el sol es cálido, pero no tan punzante como en el desierto."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1771
translate spanish d10b17_fa30cb3c:

    # "There is a weird mixture of desolation and calmness in the area, which is not surprising for a settlement this far away from Zeta."
    "Hay una extraña mezcla de desolación y calma en la zona, que no es sorprendente para un asentamiento tan alejado de Zeta."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1772
translate spanish d10b17_ea747103:

    # Zt "So... here I am..."
    Zt "Así que... aquí estoy..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1773
translate spanish d10b17_69ebaedb:

    # Zt "Another tower straight ahead, she said..."
    Zt "Otra torre más adelante, dijo..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1776
translate spanish d10b17_52d6ca16:

    # Zt "I can see it... alright then."
    Zt "Ya la veo... está bien entonces."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1779
translate spanish d10b17_9043da92:

    # "You keep going..."
    "Sigue adelante..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1782
translate spanish d10b17_efe7408d:

    # Zt "I wonder how long this place has been around for."
    Zt "Me pregunto desde cuándo existirá este lugar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1783
translate spanish d10b17_8e28683f:

    # Zt "It looks like the shacks have been patched together not too long ago..."
    Zt "Parece que las chozas han sido parchadas no hace mucho tiempo..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1786
translate spanish d10b17_e7e15de7:

    # Zt "...everything looks cobbled together, without any idea of structure."
    Zt "... todo parece improvisado, sin ninguna idea de estructura."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1787
translate spanish d10b17_232bb9b5:

    # C "Hey, you there!"
    C "¡Eh, tú!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1790
translate spanish d10b17_311a9674:

    # C "You're not from here. I would know."
    C "No eres de aquí. Yo lo sabría."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1791
translate spanish d10b17_58ead2ba:

    # C "What are you doing in this shithole?!"
    C "¿Qué haces en este agujero de mierda?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1794
translate spanish d10b17_fcbc5652:

    # "You step closer..."
    "Te acercas más..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1797
translate spanish d10b17_aba4ab3b:

    # C "Let me guess, you're looking for the big man..."
    C "Déjame adivinar, tú eres el que busca al gran hombre..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1800
translate spanish d10b17_c65bfd46:

    # Z "You got that right. And who are you?"
    Z "Lo has entendido bien. ¿Y quién eres tú?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1803
translate spanish d10b17_6d08afd0:

    # C "How sweet of you to ask."
    C "Qué amable eres al preguntar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1804
translate spanish d10b17_7663e45b:

    # C "I'm just a nobody in the desert trying to make ends meet. Like all of us here."
    C "Sólo soy un don nadie en el desierto que intenta llegar a fin de mes. Como todos los que estamos aquí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1807
translate spanish d10b17_1ad84736:

    # C "But don't mind me. If you're looking for the chief, you head this way."
    C "Pero no me hagas caso. Si buscas al jefe, dirígete hacia allí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1810
translate spanish d10b17_5eeff57d:

    # C "Don't let the blowhard intimidate you."
    C "No dejes que el fanfarrón te intimide."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1813
translate spanish d10b17_222ab108:

    # Z "{i}*chuckles*{/i} No need to worry about that."
    Z "{i}*risilla*{/i} No hay por qué preocuparse por eso."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1816
translate spanish d10b17_bd8759cf:

    # C "So... why {i}are{/i} you here, then?"
    C "Entonces... ¿por qué {i}estás{/i} aquí?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1819
translate spanish d10b17_45e94cdf:

    # Z "We can have a chat later about that. I will pay your boss a visit first."
    Z "Podemos hablar de eso más tarde. Primero iré a ver a tu jefe."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1822
translate spanish d10b17_777cad34:

    # C "Well then... don't let me stop you."
    C "Bueno, pues... no dejes que te lo impida."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1823
translate spanish d10b17_031c032a:

    # C "In case you do stick around here for some time, why not come and pay me a visit. They all do."
    C "En caso de que te quedes por aquí algún tiempo, ¿por qué no vienes a hacerme una visita? Todos lo hacen."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1824
translate spanish d10b17_6b65c99d:

    # C "Good luck for now... with whatever you're trying to do."
    C "Buena suerte por ahora... con lo que sea que intentes hacer."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1829
translate spanish d10b17_cbbe577e:

    # Z "I will think about it."
    Z "Lo pensaré."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1832
translate spanish d10b17_876a7242:

    # C "Sure... I promise you I'm not going anywhere."
    C "Claro...  Te prometo que no iré a ninguna parte."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1836
translate spanish d10b17_c584e152:

    # Z "Depends on what's on offer."
    Z "Depende de lo que se ofrezca."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1839
translate spanish d10b17_82f0650a:

    # C "I'm sure we can think of something, sweetie."
    C "Seguro que se nos ocurre algo, cariño."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1843
translate spanish d10b17_4504281b:

    # Z "I've got a wife and [persistent.da] waiting at home for me."
    Z "Tengo una esposa y una [persistent.da] esperándome en casa."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1844
translate spanish d10b17_bf121793:

    # Z "I'm sure you understand."
    Z "Estoy seguro de que lo entiendes."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1847
translate spanish d10b17_1f232ac5:

    # C "Oh, you got me wrong. Not {i}everything{/i} is about that..."
    C "Oh, me has entendido mal. No {i}todo{/i} se trata de eso..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1854
translate spanish d10b34_65781c81:

    # "You turn around..."
    "Te das la vuelta..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1857
translate spanish d10b34_df4dad30:

    # Z "Hey, I need to see your leader. I was told you'd let me through."
    Z "Oye, necesito ver a tu líder. Me dijeron que me dejarías pasar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1858
translate spanish d10b34_b11beb1f:

    # SG "Yeah... yeah... I guess I can do that."
    SG "Sí... sí... supongo que puedo hacerlo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1861
translate spanish d10b34_39309c96:

    # SG "Right this way. The first building."
    SG "Por allí. El primer edificio."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1864
translate spanish d10b34_37e2b7cf:

    # "You cross a makeshift bridge..."
    "Cruzas un puente improvisado..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1872
translate spanish d10b34_8da4965b:

    # SG "...So you could say that we increased extraction by 10%% last week."
    SG "... por lo que se puede decir que hemos aumentado la extracción en un 10%% la semana pasada."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1873
translate spanish d10b34_4e916b2e:

    # SW "See? what did I tell you."
    SW "¿Lo ves? ¿Qué te dije?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1874
translate spanish d10b34_6b6bdf95:

    # C2 "There's enough workforce out there now."
    C2 "Ya hay bastante mano de obra."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1875
translate spanish d10b34_b03922c1:

    # C2 "Tightening the belts a bit won't make them stop wanting to work here."
    C2 "Apretar un poco las correas no hará que dejen de querer trabajar aquí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1878
translate spanish d10b34_4c40d7db:

    # C2 "...and letting in some more needy fellas doesn't hurt either, isn't that right, Kitty."
    C2 "... y dejar que entren más necesitados tampoco hace daño, ¿no es así, Kitty?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1881
translate spanish d10b34_f46b5035:

    # C2 "There seems to be an infinite supply of them, indeed."
    C2 "Parece que hay un suministro infinito de ellos, de hecho."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1884
translate spanish d10b34_a1fef089:

    # C2 "She's a real lucky charm, boss. We have been doing well lately."
    C2 "Es un verdadero amuleto de la suerte, jefe. Últimamente nos va bien."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1888
translate spanish d10b34_5e513c04:

    # C2 "Who's there..."
    C2 "¿Quién está ahí...?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1889
translate spanish d10b34_93a0be0b:

    # C2 "Come in!"
    C2 "¡Entra!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1895
translate spanish d10b34_4a6e0db5:

    # Z "Are you the boss around here?"
    Z "¿Tú eres el jefe de aquí?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1898
translate spanish d10b34_402d31ea:

    # C2 "Well hello to you too, I guess..."
    C2 "Bueno, hola a ti también, supongo..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1899
translate spanish d10b34_84e23e39:

    # C2 "Yes, I am in charge of this place. You can call me the General."
    C2 "Sí, estoy a cargo de este lugar. Puedes llamarme el General."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1900
translate spanish d10b34_65ec4745:

    # Gen "Who are you? And what do you want..."
    Gen "¿Quién eres y qué quieres...?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1903
translate spanish d10b34_59ffcf99:

    # Z "Call me [persistent.player_name!c]. I was sent by the Queen of Zeta."
    Z "Llámame [persistent.player_name!c]. Me ha enviado la Reina de Zeta."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1904
translate spanish d10b34_21c4be96:

    # Z "A caravan was raided en route to this settlement, and I would like to hear what you have to say about it."
    Z "Una caravana fue asaltada de camino a este asentamiento, y me gustaría escuchar lo que tienes que decir al respecto."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1907
translate spanish d10b34_086add58:

    # Gen "I didn't know this was an interrogation."
    Gen "No sabía que esto era un interrogatorio."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1908
translate spanish d10b34_ee82ef97:

    # Gen "Yes, a caravan was raided not far from here. What is it to you?"
    Gen "Sí, una caravana fue asaltada no muy lejos de aquí. ¿Qué piensas al respecto?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1911
translate spanish d10b34_43d8a769:

    # Gen "We lost a few trading opportunities with it. Nothing irreplaceable; nothing your precious Queen should get her knickers in a twist about."
    Gen "Hemos perdido algunas oportunidades de comercio con ello. Nada insustituible; nada por lo que tu preciada Reina deba ponerse nerviosa."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1914
translate spanish d10b34_22a9da84:

    # Z "You're wrong. That caravan was one of the Queen's, and travelled under the protection of her name, which makes her knickers very much twisted."
    Z "Te equivocas. Esa caravana era de la Reina, y viajaba bajo la protección de su nombre, lo que hace que sus bragas se retuerzan mucho."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1915
translate spanish d10b34_8bbf5590:

    # Z "When Queen Merneith of Zeta is unhappy, she spreads that unhappiness across all who are concerned, with a shovel."
    Z "Cuando la Reina Merneith de Zeta está descontenta, ella esparce esa infelicidad entre todos los interesados, con una pala."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1916
translate spanish d10b34_56d27128:

    # Z "And yeah... I am the shovel, today."
    Z "Y sí... hoy yo, soy esa pala."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1917
translate spanish d10b34_de20d822:

    # Z "So you should be concerned about that caravan. And I am sure you already looked into the matter and took measures to prevent future incidents."
    Z "Así que deberías preocuparte por esa caravana. Y estoy seguro de que ya has investigado el asunto y has tomado medidas para evitar futuros incidentes."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1920
translate spanish d10b34_3671c110:

    # Gen "I'm running a business here. I won't spare able-bodied men to go look around for a caravan that is as good as gone."
    Gen "Dirijo un negocio aquí. No voy a prescindir de hombres sanos para ir a buscar una caravana que ya no existe."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1921
translate spanish d10b34_2cf3191f:

    # Gen "Honestly, I don't even understand why the Queen thought it's a good idea to send one of her lapdogs here."
    Gen "Sinceramente, ni siquiera entiendo por qué la Reina ha pensado que es una buena idea enviar a uno de sus perros falderos aquí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1922
translate spanish d10b34_5d5e1953:

    # Gen "We don't even need those caravans anyway. Got enough going for us."
    Gen "De todos modos, ni siquiera necesitamos esas caravanas. Ya tenemos bastante con lo nuestro."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1925
translate spanish d10b34_34f1b178:

    # SG "The boss is none too interested on prolonging the trade agreement, especially if it means bending the knee to Zeta."
    SG "El jefe no está demasiado interesado en prolongar el acuerdo comercial, especialmente si eso significa doblar la rodilla ante Zeta."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1928
translate spanish d10b34_c030ef24:

    # Z "The way I see it, you are living under the shadow of Zeta and enjoy a fair measure of protection simply by being in its area of influence, but you're dangerously close to the border."
    Z "Tal y como yo lo veo, vivís bajo la sombra de Zeta y disfrutáis de una buena medida de protección simplemente por estar en su zona de influencia, pero estáis peligrosamente cerca de la frontera."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1929
translate spanish d10b34_286265df:

    # Z "Raiders are getting more daring, and it's wise for you to be on her good terms, rather than counting on the few guards I've seen moping about the gates."
    Z "Los asaltantes son cada vez más atrevidos, y es conveniente que estés en sus buenos términos, en lugar de contar con los pocos guardias que he visto abatidos en las puertas."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1930
translate spanish d10b34_51965955:

    # Z "I would think twice about wanting to fight them alone, if push comes to shove..."
    Z "Me lo pensaría dos veces antes de querer luchar contra ellos solo, si se diera el caso..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1934
translate spanish d10b34_a9389493:

    # Gen "Another visitor?"
    Gen "¿Otro visitante?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1935
translate spanish d10b34_581c7fe7:

    # SG "Who's there!"
    SG "¿Quién está ahí?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1938
translate spanish d10b34_fa7c1357:

    # SW "I... I was let through, General."
    SW "Yo...  Me dejaron pasar, General."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1941
translate spanish d10b34_a92e66bc:

    # SW "I was told I could see her..."
    SW "Me dijeron que podía verla..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1944
translate spanish d10b34_6f71efb1:

    # Gen "And you even brought a donation. I hope you brought enough...?"
    Gen "Y hasta has traído un donativo. Espero que hayas traído suficiente...?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1947
translate spanish d10b34_963c5fc6:

    # SW "I... put aside what I could, General..."
    SW "Yo... aparté lo que pude, General..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1950
translate spanish d10b34_e90cf185:

    # SW "Can I... see her from up close?"
    SW "¿Puedo... verla de cerca?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1951
translate spanish d10b34_4867a7b0:

    # SG "Our Kitty is a fragile creature, worker..."
    SG "Nuestra gatita es una criatura frágil, trabajador..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1952
translate spanish d10b34_481f6c63:

    # SG "What makes you think you deserve to disturb her?"
    SG "¿Qué te hace pensar que mereces molestarla?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1953
translate spanish d10b34_07c27289:

    # Gen "Hey now... let's give this man a chance..."
    Gen "Eh... vamos a darle una oportunidad a este hombre..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1956
translate spanish d10b34_67319b8e:

    # Gen "You can see her just fine from there. Do you want to get even closer this time?"
    Gen "Desde ahí puedes verla bien. ¿Quieres acercarte aún más esta vez?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1959
translate spanish d10b34_b0f0a2fa:

    # SW "If I could, yes."
    SW "Si pudiera, sí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1962
translate spanish d10b34_8bb05bd3:

    # Gen "Alright, you brought a donation, I guess."
    Gen "Muy bien, has traído una donación, supongo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1963
translate spanish d10b34_0de51d9a:

    # Gen "But be quick about it..."
    Gen "Pero date prisa..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1966
translate spanish d10b34_b9e842f5:

    # Gen "Kitty's a gift. Flawless, innocent..."
    Gen "Kitty es un regalo. Impecable, inocente..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1967
translate spanish d10b34_a53b4e8d:

    # Gen "You know what she does not deserve?"
    Gen "¿Sabes lo que no se merece?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1968
translate spanish d10b34_d9743cd2:

    # SW "Yes, General. She should never have to waste her gift..."
    SW "Sí, General. Ella nunca debería desperdiciar su don..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1969
translate spanish d10b34_bf62ed80:

    # Gen "You got that right..."
    Gen "Tienes razón..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1972
translate spanish d10b34_7fcfd2b0:

    # Gen "Don't take it personally, but we all want her luck to be with us for a long time to come..."
    Gen "No te lo tomes como algo personal, pero todos queremos que su suerte nos acompañe durante mucho tiempo..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1973
translate spanish d10b34_6d48191b:

    # Gen "...she can never be touched by the dirty hands of a mere wastelander."
    Gen "... nunca podrá ser tocada por las sucias manos de un simple baldío."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1976
translate spanish d10b34_1b41e547:

    # SG "As the boss said... just looking, no touching."
    SG "Como dijo el jefe... sólo mirar, no tocar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1977
translate spanish d10b34_4772f3d0:

    # SG "Try something stupid and you'll leave the Overpass headfirst."
    SG "Intenta algo estúpido y saldrás de cabeza del Paso Elevado."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1980
translate spanish d10b34_f22cc2ba:

    # Gen "Alright then... get up, girl."
    Gen "Muy bien, entonces... levántate, chica."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1983
translate spanish d10b34_5e990086:

    # Kit "..."
    Kit "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1984
translate spanish d10b34_abfe98a0:

    # SW "Oh... wow..."
    SW "Oh... vaya..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1987
translate spanish d10b34_34a950d9:

    # SW "You... you are even prettier up close..."
    SW "Tú... eres aún más hermosa de cerca..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1988
translate spanish d10b34_8f43ab72:

    # SW "My name is... Vaclar, I know you probably don't care, but..."
    SW "Mi nombre es...  Vaclar, sé que probablemente no te importe, pero..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1991
translate spanish d10b34_5e990086_1:

    # Kit "..."
    Kit "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1992
translate spanish d10b34_18450c2c:

    # Vac "Oh, you..."
    Vac "Oh, tú..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1993
translate spanish d10b34_14f9c194:

    # Vac "Do you hear me?"
    Vac "¿Me has oído?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1994
translate spanish d10b34_f5a79f5a:

    # SG "Keep it cool, dude. Say what you wanted to say to her."
    SG "Mantén la calma, amigo. Di lo que querías decirle."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1997
translate spanish d10b34_d470ca74:

    # Vac "I just... wanted to say that I have been to many places, but that I have never seen someone as beautiful as you."
    Vac "Sólo... quería decirte que he estado en muchos lugares, pero que nunca he visto a alguien tan hermosa como tú."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:1998
translate spanish d10b34_6b94ee3b:

    # Vac "If I could... give you anything, I would not hesitate."
    Vac "Si pudiera... darte algo, no lo dudaría."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2001
translate spanish d10b34_d3dbffd1:

    # Vac "I wish I could see your face, but I understand that you are sheltered from the ugliness of this world..."
    Vac "Desearía poder ver tu cara, pero entiendo que estás protegida de la fealdad de este mundo..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2002
translate spanish d10b34_924a2ae8:

    # Vac "You are precious..."
    Vac "Eres preciosa..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2005
translate spanish d10b34_ee94b5df:

    # Vac "If I could just ask...-"
    Vac "Si pudiera pedir... -"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2008
translate spanish d10b34_059d6888:

    # SG "Na ah ah! What are you trying to do?!"
    SG "¡Eh eh eh! ¿Qué estás intentando hacer?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2009
translate spanish d10b34_b1ffe78d:

    # SG "Get that filthy hand away from her or you'll regret it!"
    SG "¡Aleja esa asquerosa mano de ella o te arrepentirás!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2012
translate spanish d10b34_7760e308:

    # Vac "I am sorry... I didn't want to scare her."
    Vac "Lo siento...  No quería asustarla."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2015
translate spanish d10b34_84a38c25:

    # Gen "Well stay away from her then..."
    Gen "Pues aléjate de ella entonces..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2018
translate spanish d10b34_6085df1d:

    # Vac "Can I... ask something of her?"
    Vac "¿Puedo... pedirle algo?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2021
translate spanish d10b34_17c3b464:

    # Gen "Your donation only gets you so much time, man..."
    Gen "Tu donación sólo te da tiempo, tío.."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2024
translate spanish d10b34_03fdb8c2:

    # Vac "I always... this is embarrassing..."
    Vac "Siempre... esto es vergonzoso..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2027
translate spanish d10b34_0c1bdc5f:

    # SG "I'm sure it is, just spit it out already."
    SG "Estoy seguro de que es así, escúpelo de una vez."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2028
translate spanish d10b34_fbeebb64:

    # Vac "I would ask if she could bless me with her luck, by name."
    Vac "Le pediría que me bendijera con su suerte, por su nombre."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2029
translate spanish d10b34_898cc6e3:

    # Gen "Now you're just being rude..."
    Gen "Ahora sólo estás siendo grosero..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2030
translate spanish d10b34_f55d1c73:

    # SG "Just say the word, boss."
    SG "Sólo di la palabra, jefe."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2033
translate spanish d10b34_5f976ee8:

    # Gen "Tell you what... you have one week to bring two extra loads of coal to us, and we will see if she can grant you a bit of added good fortune just for you."
    Gen "Te diré que... tienes una semana para traernos dos cargas extra de carbón, y veremos si puede concederte un poco más de fortuna sólo para ti."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2034
translate spanish d10b34_70eece1e:

    # Gen "What do you say?"
    Gen "¿Qué dices?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2037
translate spanish d10b34_8d50298f:

    # Vac "Re... really?"
    Vac "En... ¿en serio?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2038
translate spanish d10b34_c5df3c43:

    # Vac "I mean, yes... I would love to..."
    Vac "Quiero decir, sí...  Me encantaría..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2041
translate spanish d10b34_e07bec72:

    # Gen "Alright then... Kitty, this man, Vaclar, is going to ask special attention from you, a week from now. You understand?"
    Gen "Muy bien, entonces...  Kitty, este hombre, Vaclar, va a pedirte una atención especial, dentro de una semana. ¿Entiendes?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2047
translate spanish d10b34_5e990086_2:

    # Kit "..."
    Kit "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2048
translate spanish d10b34_fff7b194:

    # "For a moment, it looks like she is about to say something, before closing her mouth again."
    "Por un momento, parece que está a punto de decir algo, antes de volver a cerrar la boca."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2051
translate spanish d10b34_24cf9f38:

    # Vac "She acknowledged me..."
    Vac "Ella me reconoció..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2052
translate spanish d10b34_2414d610:

    # Gen "You happy?"
    Gen "¿Estás contento?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2053
translate spanish d10b34_8213fe9b:

    # Vac "Yes I am, General, thank you..."
    Vac "Sí, General, gracias..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2054
translate spanish d10b34_5e86b84e:

    # Gen "Good."
    Gen "Bien."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2057
translate spanish d10b34_a11c9fd6:

    # Gen "Then make sure you remember... one week, two extra loads."
    Gen "Entonces asegúrate de recordar... una semana, dos cargas extra."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2058
translate spanish d10b34_7ecb024c:

    # Gen "Kitty is counting on you, you don't want her to be unhappy."
    Gen "Kitty cuenta contigo, no querrás que sea infeliz."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2061
translate spanish d10b34_7547a85d:

    # Vac "I cannot thank you enough."
    Vac "No podría agradecértelo lo suficiente."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2062
translate spanish d10b34_c33dd938:

    # Vac "And I will bring you the donations requested."
    Vac "Y te traeré las donaciones solicitadas."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2063
translate spanish d10b34_648d723e:

    # Vac "I will see you again soon, I hope."
    Vac "Espero volver a verte pronto."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2066
translate spanish d10b34_87d704c1:

    # SG "Alright, that's about enough. She needs to rest."
    SG "Muy bien, ya es suficiente. Ella necesita descansar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2067
translate spanish d10b34_d3b8e160:

    # SG "The mine is still open; you should get back to work."
    SG "La mina sigue abierta, deberías volver al trabajo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2071
translate spanish d10b34_e9368717:

    # "As the girl sits back down, the worker leaves the room..."
    "Mientras la chica vuelve a sentarse, el trabajador sale de la habitación..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2074
translate spanish d10b34_4ad4b087:

    # Gen "So, now that you've seen how things go around here..."
    Gen "Así que, ahora que has visto cómo van las cosas por aquí..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2075
translate spanish d10b34_cedcc6d0:

    # Gen "Tell me again, why would I need anything from the Queen, when I have my own show to run?!"
    Gen "Dímelo otra vez, ¿por qué iba a necesitar algo de la Reina, ¡¿cuando puedo dirigir mi propio espectáculo?!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2078
translate spanish d10b34_19273b16:

    # Gen "...you better give me a good reason to not kick you out of this room myself, \"ambassador\"..."
    Gen "... más vale que me des una buena razón para no echarte yo mismo de esta habitación, \"embajador\"..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2087
translate spanish d10b44_99a9de3d:

    # Z "You think charades like this will make this settlement flourish?"
    Z "¿Crees que farsas como esta harán florecer este asentamiento?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2088
translate spanish d10b44_ba32a856:

    # Z "What do you have here, some workers mining the coal and you getting something off the top?"
    Z "¿Qué tienes aquí, unos trabajadores extrayendo el carbón y tú sacando algo de provecho?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2089
translate spanish d10b44_9c1959a0:

    # Z "What are you going to do with it, burn it?!"
    Z "¿Qué vas a hacer con eso, quemarlo?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2090
translate spanish d10b44_c139c51c:

    # Z "You can't eat it and you need trade to continue passing through here. The Queen might decide that she prefers caravans to follow a different route, if you don't do your part."
    Z "No puedes comerlo y necesitas el comercio para seguir transitando por aquí. La Reina podría decidir que prefiere que las caravanas sigan otra ruta, si no cumples tu parte."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2093
translate spanish d10b44_c2e087a3:

    # Gen "I knew I hated you the moment you stepped foot in here."
    Gen "Sabía que te odiaba desde el momento en que pusiste un pie aquí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2094
translate spanish d10b44_3f4c0104:

    # Gen "Listen closely you Zetan fuck..."
    Gen "Escucha atentamente, maldito zetano..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2097
translate spanish d10b44_f2564155:

    # Gen "First, this settlement doesn't thrive just on me showing her off to people for coin or coal. There are other buyers out there too."
    Gen "En primer lugar, este acuerdo no prospera sólo con que yo la muestre a la gente a cambio de monedas o carbón. También hay otros compradores."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2098
translate spanish d10b44_19b2347d:

    # Gen "Your city is not the center of the world."
    Gen "Tu ciudad no es el centro del mundo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2099
translate spanish d10b44_69ff23af:

    # Gen "Second, Kitty's my little sister, and you don't get to offend her."
    Gen "En segundo lugar, Kitty es mi hermana pequeña, y no puedes ofenderla."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2100
translate spanish d10b44_ff98da55:

    # Gen "People respect her for what she is, and people gladly pay to keep her the way she is. She is our good luck charm."
    Gen "La gente la respeta por lo que es, y la gente paga gustosamente para que siga siendo como es. Es nuestro amuleto de buena suerte."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2103
translate spanish d10b44_69c2de7e:

    # Gen "If you have a problem with the way the place works, that's a you problem. We're not forcing anyone to pay anything."
    Gen "Si tienes algún problema con el funcionamiento de este lugar, es un problema tuyo. No estamos obligando a nadie a pagar nada."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2104
translate spanish d10b44_0d599ff2:

    # Gen "We take a simple tax on all the coal that is mined here, and make sure that the gates are safe from unruly thugs."
    Gen "Cobramos un simple impuesto por todo el carbón que se extrae aquí, y nos aseguramos de que las puertas estén a salvo de los matones revoltosos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2105
translate spanish d10b44_51dab8e8:

    # Gen "My little treasure is just an added value to this."
    Gen "Mi pequeño tesoro es sólo un valor añadido a esto."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2108
translate spanish d10b44_1042e4a4:

    # SG "Boss pays us well, people come here for a safe place to work..."
    SG "El jefe nos paga bien, la gente viene aquí por un lugar seguro para trabajar..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2109
translate spanish d10b44_8b619584:

    # Gen "It just works, you see."
    Gen "Simplemente funciona, ya ves."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2112
translate spanish d10b44_c0176ffe:

    # Gen "Now... the last thing we need is some regulations, inhibitions, or taxes imposed by your city..."
    Gen "Ahora... lo último que necesitamos son algunas regulaciones o inhibiciones, o tributos impuestos por tu ciudad..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2115
translate spanish d10b44_d53e54f0:

    # Z "You still don't see the larger picture, do you?!"
    Z "Sigues sin ver el panorama general, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2116
translate spanish d10b44_c7e69ac0:

    # Z "The attacks are getting closer and closer; your little overpass won't be safe forever on its own."
    Z "Los ataques están cada vez más cerca, tu pequeño paso elevado no estará siempre a salvo por sí solo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2119
translate spanish d10b44_947878c2:

    # Gen "This is a good place to seek shelter from storms, to find water and for caravans to stop by, and not just Zeta's caravans."
    Gen "Este es un buen lugar para refugiarse de las tormentas, para encontrar agua y para que paren las caravanas, y no sólo las de Zeta."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2120
translate spanish d10b44_1bf93429:

    # Gen "We don't need you. Our agreement with your Queen is over, so don't lay her problems at our doorstep."
    Gen "No te necesitamos. Nuestro acuerdo con tu Reina ha terminado, así que no nos eches en cara sus problemas."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2121
translate spanish d10b44_c7f1c838:

    # Gen "The raiders have no reason to trouble us. What do they want with coal anyway? Caravans will have to fend for themselves, as they always have."
    Gen "Los asaltantes no tienen motivos para molestarnos. Además, ¿para qué quieren el carbón? Las caravanas tendrán que valerse por sí mismas, como siempre."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2124
translate spanish d10b44_1427d813:

    # Gen "Now, have you anything else to say before I kick you out of this room?!"
    Gen "Ahora, ¿tienes algo más que decir antes de que te eche de esta habitación?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2130
translate spanish d10b44_e920a7c2:

    # Z "Don't expect the Queen to be happy about this."
    Z "No esperes que la Reina se alegre de esto."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2133
translate spanish d10b44_0fd3e898:

    # Gen "So fucking what?"
    Gen "¿Y qué coño?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2134
translate spanish d10b44_c29051ae:

    # Gen "What is she going to do, come here and take this place over?"
    Gen "¿Qué es lo que va a hacer, venir aquí y apoderarse de este lugar?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2137
translate spanish d10b44_7e70dc2d:

    # Gen "Besides, let's be honest, if the Queen wanted this place for herself, she would've already sent an army."
    Gen "Además, seamos sinceros, si la Reina quisiera este lugar para ella, ya habría enviado un ejército."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2138
translate spanish d10b44_58b04534:

    # Gen "But as far as I know, building up an enclave herself is too troublesome, so instead she needs a lackey."
    Gen "Pero por lo que sé, construir un enclave ella misma es demasiado problemático, así que en su lugar necesita un lacayo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2141
translate spanish d10b44_0aa1f360:

    # Gen "So take a walk through the town; take your time and see for yourself."
    Gen "Así que date un paseo por la ciudad, tómate tu tiempo y compruébalo tú mismo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2144
translate spanish d10b44_d8f2d67b:

    # Gen "...and then tell your Queen to go and fuck herself thoroughly."
    Gen "... y luego le dices a tu Reina que se folle a sí misma a fondo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2145
translate spanish d10b44_b132efa9:

    # Gen "Now get out!"
    Gen "¡Ahora fuera!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2149
translate spanish d10b44_5a4836fb:

    # Z "You're going to regret this."
    Z "Te vas a arrepentir de esto."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2150
translate spanish d10b44_d5dac5f8:

    # Z "I don't know when or how, but you're going to wish you made a different choice when you were still in the position to make one."
    Z "No sé cuándo ni cómo, pero desearás haber tomado una decisión diferente cuando aún estabas en condiciones de hacerlo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2153
translate spanish d10b44_ba7e35c7:

    # Gen "Big fucking mouth for someone standing in another man's home, don't you think?"
    Gen "Una jodida boca grande para alguien que está en casa de otro, ¿no crees?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2154
translate spanish d10b44_4e9c0024:

    # Gen "If it wasn't more trouble than it's worth, I'd be throwing you off the Overpass myself."
    Gen "Si no fuera más problema de lo que vale, yo mismo te tiraría por el Paso Elevado."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2157
translate spanish d10b44_9c78a642:

    # Gen "But no, I unfortunately can't do that without causing a ruckus. But this conversation is over."
    Gen "Pero no, desgraciadamente no puedo hacerlo sin causar un escándalo. Pero esta conversación ha terminado.."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2158
translate spanish d10b44_69e0a40d:

    # Gen "Fuck off out of here..."
    Gen "Vete a tomar por el culo de aquí..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2159
translate spanish d10b44_f07af207:

    # Gen "...and make sure you let your Queen know that I don't give a shit about her."
    Gen "... y asegúrate de hacer saber a tu Reina que ella me importa una mierda."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2165
translate spanish d10b80_46790e38:

    # "You head out into the blistering heat..."
    "Te diriges al calor abrasador..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2168
translate spanish d10b80_e36976b6:

    # Zt "I guess that's that."
    Zt "Supongo que eso es todo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2169
translate spanish d10b80_0f21cf03:

    # Zt "It doesn't seem like anything will go through that guy's thick head."
    Zt "No parece que nada vaya a pasar por la espesa cabeza de ese tipo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2173
translate spanish d10b80_225f4235:

    # Zt "I should head back and tell the Queen that sending anyone here is pointless, there's no deal to be had."
    Zt "Debería volver y decirle a la Reina que enviar a alguien aquí no tiene sentido, que no hay trato que hacer."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2178
translate spanish d10b80_41ecf7be:

    # "You hear chatting from the tower..."
    "Oyes una charla en la torre..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2182
translate spanish d10b80_1d33cf9a:

    # SG "...I know... but..."
    SG "... Lo sé... pero..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2183
translate spanish d10b80_3fdd484f:

    # SG2 "No buts, fuck it. You're a guard. Where I am from, we shoot people when they say that."
    SG2 "Sin peros, a la mierda. Eres un guardia. De donde yo vengo, disparamos a la gente cuando dice eso."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2184
translate spanish d10b80_9152031d:

    # SG "Yeah, about that..."
    SG "Sí, sobre eso..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2186
translate spanish d10b80_786ce1eb:

    # SG "...I don't know where he is, but I will ask around."
    SG "... No sé dónde está, pero preguntaré por ahí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2187
translate spanish d10b80_1bea181f:

    # SG2 "Maybe he's with the boss."
    SG2 "Tal vez esté con el jefe."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2188
translate spanish d10b80_9072b7cd:

    # SG2 "Let him know that I'll kick his ass if he doesn't show up for his shift."
    SG2 "Que sepa que le daré una patada en el culo si no se presenta a su turno"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2189
translate spanish d10b80_3f64c4c6:

    # SG "Will do..."
    SG "Lo haré..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2190
translate spanish d10b80_68f60f97:

    # SG "Hey, Stalker!"
    SG "¡Eh, Acechador!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2193
translate spanish d10b80_7053cc2c:

    # SG "What, are you going to head out already?!"
    SG "¿Qué, vas a salir ya?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2194
translate spanish d10b80_4e848710:

    # Z "I've talked to your boss. My work here is done."
    Z "He hablado con tu jefe. Mi trabajo aquí ha terminado."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2197
translate spanish d10b80_989553bf:

    # Z "I hope everything's still in there."
    Z "Espero que todo siga ahí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2200
translate spanish d10b80_bbfccd2b:

    # SG2 "Don't worry about that. Even if we were mighty curious, we have rules here."
    SG2 "No te preocupes por eso. Aunque seamos muy curiosos, aquí tenemos reglas."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2203
translate spanish d10b80_87026302:

    # SG2 "If you want to get out, you have to wait till the next shift is on duty."
    SG2 "Si quieres salir, tendrás que esperar a que el siguiente turno esté de guardia."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2204
translate spanish d10b80_a53aeafa:

    # SG2 "I'm not supposed to open the gate on my own, and well..."
    SG2 "No se supone que deba abrir la puerta por mi cuenta, y bueno..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2206
translate spanish d10b80_11a60784:

    # SG2 "I don't think my friend likes you enough after what you said..."
    SG2 "... no creo que mi amigo te quiera lo suficiente después de lo que has dicho..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2208
translate spanish d10b80_bb909f0b:

    # SG2 "Looks like my friend is just leaving the post. Gotta wait it out."
    SG2 "... parece que mi amigo está dejando el puesto. Habrá que esperar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2212
translate spanish d10b80_fa4e51b7:

    # SG "Let's forget about that now, alright."
    SG "Olvidemos eso ahora, de acuerdo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2214
translate spanish d10b80_c6c1cab9:

    # SG "It won't take long; I will go get him."
    SG "No tardaré mucho, iré a buscarlo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2218
translate spanish d10b80_134d72be:

    # SG "Thanks again, Fardin... for everything."
    SG "Gracias de nuevo, Fardin... por todo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2219
translate spanish d10b80_be860c84:

    # SG2 "Don't worry about it, let me know if you want to hang out after work!"
    SG2 "No te preocupes, ¡avísame si quieres salir después del trabajo!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2221
translate spanish d10b80_6199de19:

    # SG "By the way, thanks Fardin. For not making me wait for him."
    SG "Por cierto, gracias Fardin. Por no hacerme esperar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2222
translate spanish d10b80_76277475:

    # SG2 "Hey, it's not your fault that he's missing the shift."
    SG2 "Oye, no es culpa tuya que pierda el turno."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2223
translate spanish d10b80_b64cf263:

    # SG2 "Let me know if you want to hang out some time!"
    SG2 "Avísame si quieres salir algún día."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2226
translate spanish d10b80_bbbd5ffa:

    # SG "..."
    SG "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2232
translate spanish d10b80_26a803bc:

    # C "..."
    C "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2233
translate spanish d10b80_d8e2e549:

    # Zt "Wait... isn't that..."
    Zt "Espera... esa no es..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2236
translate spanish d10b80_26a803bc_1:

    # C "..."
    C "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2239
translate spanish d10b80_81d6508e:

    # "She went inside..."
    "Ella entró en el interior..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2243
translate spanish d10b80_e2752575:

    # "You follow her..."
    "La sigues..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2247
translate spanish d10b80_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2250
translate spanish d10b80_eaf4d1ad:

    # Z "I expected many things..."
    Z "Esperaba muchas cosas..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2251
translate spanish d10b80_6804ae07:

    # Z "But to see you here?"
    Z "¿Pero verte aquí?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2255
translate spanish d10b80_dd7552ca:

    # Ky "Funny coincidence, isn't it...?"
    Ky "Curiosa coincidencia, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2256
translate spanish d10b80_5888e2df:

    # Ky "I can tell you why."
    Ky "Puedo decirte por qué."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2257
translate spanish d10b80_de161307:

    # Ky "Asha and the others are waiting for me."
    Ky "Asha y los demás me están esperando."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2258
translate spanish d10b80_009de2d3:

    # Ky "They're preparing an attack and I need to be there with them."
    Ky "Están preparando un ataque y tengo que estar allí con ellos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2261
translate spanish d10b80_0ff66d77:

    # Z "Wait, what did you just say?!"
    Z "Espera, ¿qué acabas de decir?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2264
translate spanish d10b80_e06daeed:

    # Ky "I'm not sure why that is..."
    Ky "No estoy segura de que eso sea así..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2271
translate spanish d10b80_f7e35766:

    # Z "Fancy meeting a friendly raider face here."
    Z "Me alegro de encontrarme con una cara amistosa de una asaltante."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2274
translate spanish d10b80_01279dc7:

    # Ky "Hm..."
    Ky "Hm..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2277
translate spanish d10b80_e02f1956:

    # Ky "What, in my face, says friendly to you?"
    Ky "¿Qué, de mi cara, te parece amigable?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2278
translate spanish d10b80_1ff76d4b:

    # Z "What can I say? I have low standards..."
    Z "¿Qué puedo decir? Tengo un nivel de exigencia bajo..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2281
translate spanish d10b80_c0a86d20:

    # Ky "That's what I'm thinking."
    Ky "Eso es lo que estaba pensando."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2287
translate spanish d10b80_c8d21307:

    # Z "What the hell? Why are you here?"
    Z "¿Qué demonios? ¿Por qué estás aquí?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2290
translate spanish d10b80_f53c0036:

    # Ky "Well, hello to you too, and fuck you."
    Ky "Bueno, hola a ti también, y que te den."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2291
translate spanish d10b80_e52a22e9:

    # Z "Prickly as ever, I see."
    Z "Más espinosa que nunca, por lo que veo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2294
translate spanish d10b80_3190db36:

    # Ky "As if you don't enjoy it..."
    Ky "Como si no lo disfrutaras..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2300
translate spanish d10b105_0c172790:

    # Ky "{i}*kissing*"
    Ky "{i}*beso*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2303
translate spanish d10b105_f9a65257:

    # "You push her to the wall..."
    "La empujas contra la pared..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2304
translate spanish d10b105_b83651ee:

    # Ky "Mhh..."
    Ky "Mhh..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2307
translate spanish d10b105_35a67ac3:

    # Ky "..."
    Ky "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2308
translate spanish d10b105_687928c6:

    # "The only sound in the room is that of your kisses. Under your expert touch, the tough Raider leader softens, as her tongue plays with yours."
    "El único sonido en la habitación es el de tus besos. Bajo tu toque experto, la dura líder de los Raiders se ablanda, mientras su lengua juega con la tuya."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2311
translate spanish d10b105_7d6b0b00:

    # "You start making out increasingly more aggressive, and you suddenly put your hand inside her pants."
    "Empezáis a besaros de forma cada vez más agresiva, y de repente le metes la mano dentro de sus pantalones."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2314
translate spanish d10b105_96b90cc8:

    # Kyw "{i}*gasp*{/i}..."
    Kyw "{i}*jadeos*{/i}..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2315
translate spanish d10b105_41d48e6a:

    # Kyw "You are getting handsy I see..."
    Kyw "Ya veo que te pones manos a la obra..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2318
translate spanish d10b105_c09b8289:

    # Ky "Ngh... {i}*kissing*"
    Ky "Ngh...  {i}*beso*"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2324
translate spanish d10b105_35a67ac3_1:

    # Ky "..."
    Ky "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2325
translate spanish d10b105_af287e44:

    # "She stares at you as you make your movement, mesmerised."
    "Ella te mira fijamente mientras haces tu movimiento, hipnotizada."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2328
translate spanish d10b105_530831ce:

    # "You slowly pull down her skirt more and more, and her breathing intensifies."
    "Le bajas lentamente la ropa cada vez más, y su respiración se intensifica."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2331
translate spanish d10b105_b83651ee_1:

    # Ky "Mhh..."
    Ky "Mhh..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2332
translate spanish d10b105_35a67ac3_2:

    # Ky "..."
    Ky "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2335
translate spanish d10b105_c1016cb3:

    # Ky "No! Asha!"
    Ky "¡No! ¡Asha!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2338
translate spanish d10b105_d3e84d0f:

    # Ky "Sorry, baby... we can't fuck around here. Not now at least..."
    Ky "Lo siento, cariño... no podemos joder aquí. Al menos ahora no..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2339
translate spanish d10b105_01422cf1:

    # Ky "Asha and the others are waiting. They're preparing the attack and I need to be there with them."
    Ky "Asha y los demás están esperando. Están preparando el ataque y tengo que estar allí con ellos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2340
translate spanish d10b105_cf58ea59:

    # Ky "We don't want them to think I got captured or some shit..."
    Ky "No queremos que piensen que me han capturado o algo así..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2343
translate spanish d10b105_0ff66d77:

    # Z "Wait, what did you just say?!"
    Z "Espera, ¿qué acabas de decir?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2349
translate spanish d10b111_8ec93ff1:

    # Z "You're going to destroy this place? I'm here to prevent that shit!"
    Z "¿Vas a destruir este lugar? ¡Estoy aquí para evitar esa mierda!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2352
translate spanish d10b111_6ec9f449:

    # Ky "And why's that? Who sent you here?"
    Ky "¿Y por qué? ¿Quién te ha enviado aquí?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2355
translate spanish d10b111_6b22ce3a:

    # Z "Who do you think sent me here? I will give you a hint, she is a Queen..."
    Z "¿Quién crees que me ha enviado aquí? Te daré una pista, es una Reina..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2356
translate spanish d10b111_301ea4f9:

    # Z "Let me guess, you were also responsible for raiding that caravan?"
    Z "Déjame adivinar, ¿también fuiste el responsable de asaltar esa caravana?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2359
translate spanish d10b111_49b037f5:

    # Ky "Yeah, why not? They were easy prey. And we're taking down this General cocksucker next."
    Ky "Sí, ¿por qué no? Eran presas fáciles. Y lo siguiente será acabar con ese chupapollas del General."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2362
translate spanish d10b111_7f0cda07:

    # Z "{i}*sigh*{/i} You're fucking kidding. Okay, listen."
    Z "{i}*suspiro*{/i} Estás de coña. Vale, escucha."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2363
translate spanish d10b111_fc15a508:

    # Z "If you raid this place, the Queen will not take it too kindly..."
    Z "Si asaltas este lugar, la Reina no se lo tomará muy bien..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2366
translate spanish d10b111_838c7563:

    # Ky "That's unfortunate. I almost feel bad for her..."
    Ky "Es lamentable. Casi me siento mal por ella..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2369
translate spanish d10b111_7d6177cb:

    # Z "Yeah, except it's not that simple. She will come down hard on you, and I am sure you have better things to do than trying to evade an entire army."
    Z "Sí, pero no es tan sencillo. Ella se ensañará contigo, y estoy seguro de que tienes mejores cosas que hacer que intentar evadir a todo un ejército."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2370
translate spanish d10b111_540da990:

    # Z "But she could turn a blind eye to a simple change in leadership."
    Z "Pero ella podría hacer oídos sordos a un simple cambio de liderazgo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2371
translate spanish d10b111_1ce6394b:

    # Z "As long as certain things stayed the same..."
    Z "Siempre que ciertas cosas sigan igual..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2374
translate spanish d10b111_b6390adc:

    # Ky "You can try to convince me, [persistent.player_name]. But I have a gang waiting for me. You haven't met them."
    Ky "Puedes intentar convencerme, [persistent.player_name]. Pero tengo una banda esperándome. No los has conocido."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2375
translate spanish d10b111_54cfcd3f:

    # Ky "They've been waiting for hours, and I can't and won't stop them."
    Ky "Llevan horas esperando y no puedo ni quiero detenerlos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2378
translate spanish d10b111_363aee24:

    # Z "{i}*sigh*{/i}... Shit."
    Z "{i}*suspiro*{/i}...  Mierda."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2379
translate spanish d10b111_4586490e:

    # Z "Listen... all the Queen needs is a reliable trading route through this place. It doesn't matter who rules this place."
    Z "Escucha... todo lo que la Reina necesita es una ruta comercial fiable a través de este lugar. No importa quién gobierne este lugar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2380
translate spanish d10b111_efbbd49d:

    # Z "Go and prepare your attack but tell your people to wait until I give a signal and leave the Overpass."
    Z "Ve y prepara tu ataque, pero dile a tu gente que espere hasta que yo dé una señal y abandone el paso elevado."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2381
translate spanish d10b111_16dc460e:

    # Z "And go easy on the settlers."
    Z "Y no te preocupes por los colonos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2384
translate spanish d10b111_d2ba0fa2:

    # Ky "What are you talking about? We don't want to run a settlement, if that's what you're hinting at!"
    Ky "¿De qué estás hablando? ¡No queremos llevar a cabo un asentamiento, si eso es lo que estás insinuando!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2385
translate spanish d10b111_c0ca9d79:

    # Ky "And how do you figure that it will keep going in the first place?"
    Ky "¿Y cómo crees que se mantendrá en primer lugar?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2386
translate spanish d10b111_c989a633:

    # Ky "Listen, I will do things your way, for now... but when the dust settles, we will have to have a proper conversation about your fucking plan."
    Ky "Escucha, haré las cosas a tu manera, por ahora... Pero cuando el polvo se asiente, tendremos que tener una conversación adecuada sobre tu maldito plan."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2389
translate spanish d10b111_0b4b5628:

    # Z "That's fine. Give me a headstart, then you do your thing and when we're in control we will talk about the future of this place."
    Z "Eso está bien. Dame un poco de ventaja, luego haz lo tuyo y cuando tengamos el control hablaremos del futuro de este lugar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2390
translate spanish d10b111_43bd69e8:

    # Z "Let me look around a bit. You will see, I will give you enough reasons to get a good foothold here, instead of having to watch your back from other gangs in Adira."
    Z "Déjame echar un vistazo. Verás, te daré suficientes razones para establecerte aquí, en lugar de tener que vigilar tu espalda por otras pandillas en Adira."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2393
translate spanish d10b111_01279dc7:

    # Ky "Hm..."
    Ky "Hm..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2394
translate spanish d10b111_771d48a4:

    # Z "What is it?"
    Z "¿Qué es lo que pasa?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2397
translate spanish d10b111_7d659413:

    # Ky "If you're going to look around... there is actually someone I know in here."
    Ky "Si vas a echar un vistazo... en realidad hay alguien aquí que conozco."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2400
translate spanish d10b111_d102dfec:

    # Ky "You saw the medical container? The girl inside, I know her. She used to run with us."
    Ky "¿Has visto el contenedor médico? La chica de dentro, la conozco. Solía correr con nosotros."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2401
translate spanish d10b111_14490634:

    # Ky "Tell her I know you, and you two can think of what to do. She knows what's going to go down."
    Ky "Dile que te conozco y que vosotros dos podéis pensar qué hacer. Ella sabe lo que va a pasar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2404
translate spanish d10b111_ad37ebcd:

    # Ky "But don't take too long, [persistent.player_name]."
    Ky "Pero no tardes mucho, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2405
translate spanish d10b111_48931cfc:

    # Ky "I may lead the gang, but I can't hold them back for too long. This place just begs to be raided."
    Ky "Puede que yo lidere la banda, pero no puedo retenerla durante mucho tiempo. Este lugar pide ser asaltado."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2408
translate spanish d10b111_27a05cb8:

    # Z "You're their leader. Keep them in check. Now get out and wait for my signal."
    Z "Tú eres su líder. Mantenlos a raya. Ahora salid y esperad mi señal."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2412
translate spanish d10b111_e1824f17:

    # "One at a time, you leave the shack and Kyra slinks away from the settlement, to meet her gang."
    "De uno en uno, salís de la choza y Kyra se aleja del asentamiento para reunirse con su banda."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2414
translate spanish d10b111_745b854f:

    # "As you look around, you wonder what impact you can have on these people's immediate future..."
    "Mientras mira a su alrededor, se pregunta qué impacto puede tener en el futuro inmediato de esta gente..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2427
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_a78f81e1:

    # Zt "This is some kind of medical center, I guess."
    Zt "Esto es una especie de centro médico, supongo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2428
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_d0d6cf75:

    # Zt "According to Kyra, this is her contact on the inside."
    Zt "Según Kyra, éste es su contacto en el interior."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2431
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_f61e7ccc:

    # "As you are about to enter, you hear mumbling from the inside. Before stepping in, you listen closely..."
    "Cuando están a punto de entrar, oyen murmullos procedentes del interior. Antes de entrar, escuchas atentamente..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2434
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_f6001570:

    # C "I'm sorry about this, but I'm pretty sure that's what's causing your pain."
    C "Lo siento, pero estoy bastante segura de que eso es lo que está causando tu dolor."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2437
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_757705c6:

    # C2 "Yeah... I guess it makes sense now..."
    C2 "Sí... supongo que ahora tiene sentido..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2440
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_5a79ed51:

    # C "While it won't get better anytime soon, the symptoms are not that severe yet."
    C "Aunque no mejorará pronto, los síntomas aún no son tan graves."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2441
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_84a4e834:

    # C "The metastasis needs time to spread. You should still be fine for several weeks at least."
    C "La\"metástasis' necesita tiempo para extenderse. Deberías estar bien al menos durante varias semanas."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2442
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_34c7a529:

    # C "If the pain gets bad, come to me. I can cook something up to ease the pain."
    C "Si el dolor se agrava, acude a mí. Puedo preparar algo para aliviar el dolor."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2445
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_3bb67751:

    # C2 "I appreciate it. Right now, I'm not hurting too bad. I hope it won't worsen too soon."
    C2 "Te lo agradezco...  Ahora mismo no me duele mucho. Espero que no empeore demasiado pronto."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2448
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_32748ec9:

    # C2 "But I'm a tough cookie. Whatever it is, I will handle it."
    C2 "Pero soy una persona dura. Sea lo que sea, podré soportarlo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2451
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_7c780555:

    # "You step in..."
    "Entras dentro.."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2454
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_2074c87c:

    # C "I wish there was more I could do. But you know how things are, around here."
    C "Ojalá pudiera hacer algo más. Pero ya sabes cómo son las cosas, por aquí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2457
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_2f0e7073:

    # C2 "You're a good woman, I know you're doing your best."
    C2 "Eres una buena mujer, sé que haces lo que puedes."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2458
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_9eacb4b5:

    # C2 "Now don't worry about me, at least I don't have to climb back down the mine anytime soon."
    C2 "No te preocupes por mí, al menos no tendré que volver a bajar a la mina por ahora"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2461
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_8b6726c1:

    # C2 "Why hello, it's you again."
    C2 "Vaya, hola, eres tú otra vez."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2462
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_32c44bba:

    # C2 "I guess I will leave you two to it."
    C2 "Supongo que os dejaré hablar a vosotros dos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2465
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_94368a74:

    # Z "I appreciate it."
    Z "Lo aprecio."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2468
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_bd559a6c:

    # "The bald woman leaves the container..."
    "La mujer calva sale del container..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2471
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_3e372920:

    # C "I'll be with you in a moment, I just need to catch a breath."
    C "Estaré contigo en un momento, sólo necesito recuperar el aliento."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2472
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_aa011151:

    # Cw "{i}*sigh*{/i} This place is going to shit."
    Cw "{i}*suspiro*{/i} Este lugar se va a la mierda."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2475
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_9598e55d:

    # Z "I'm not here for a medical exam."
    Z "No estoy aquí para un examen médico."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2476
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_3b96f032:

    # Z "Kyra told me you're a friend of hers."
    Z "Kyra me ha dicho que eres una amiga suya."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2479
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_22fd8627:

    # Z "She told me that you know... about the attack."
    Z "Me ha dicho que sabes... lo del ataque."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2480
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_7370d7ae:

    # Z "Are you really cooperating with her?"
    Z "¿Cooperas realmente con ella?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2483
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_bae44373:

    # C "Cooperating is a big word. I know her, and who she is."
    C "Cooperar es una gran palabra. La conozco y sé quién es."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2484
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_4aa206ac:

    # C "If she says they mean to take this place... they will. So, I have little choice."
    C "Si dice que quieren tomar este lugar... lo harán. Así que tengo pocas opciones."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2487
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_26a803bc:

    # C "..."
    C "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2490
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_76360a30:

    # "She gets up..."
    "Se levanta..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2493
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_423efbb9:

    # C "Look, sorry. I'm normally not like that. Let's start over."
    C "Mira, lo siento. Normalmente no soy así. Empecemos de nuevo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2494
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_83f90877:

    # C "Yes, I used to be one of the raiders from Adira. Part of a different gang. I knew Kyra because, well... you have seen her. She does not go unnoticed."
    C "Sí, antes era una de los asaltantes de Adira. Formaba parte de otra banda. Conocí a Kyra porque, bueno... la has visto. No pasa desapercibida."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2497
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_207e3c94:

    # C "But what can I say. I quit that life. Left it all behind. A pretty good idea in hindsight, seeing how downhill it went for my old gang."
    C "Pero qué puedo decir. Dejé esa vida. Lo dejé todo atrás. Una idea bastante buena en retrospectiva, viendo lo mal que le fue a mi antigua banda."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2500
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_c8fc12fe:

    # C "So, I was looking for a place to start over. I have some skill with poultices and some medical knowledge, so... the choice was easy."
    C "Buscaba un lugar para empezar de nuevo. Tengo cierta habilidad con las cataplasmas y algunos conocimientos médicos, así que... la elección fue fácil."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2501
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_7f935e4e:

    # C "I patched up the guys in Adira for years. They all called me their medic anyway. Haven't used my actual name in years."
    C "He curado a los chicos de Adira durante años. De todos modos, todos me llamaban su médica. Hace años que no uso mi nombre real."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2504
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_e1a7188a:

    # Med "So anyway. Here I am, earning my living in a settlement that treats its workers like crap..."
    Med "De todos modos. Aquí estoy, ganándome la vida en un asentamiento que trata a sus trabajadores como una mierda..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2507
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_bdbb03a4:

    # Med "...and before I know it, the craziest people of my old life come knocking on the door."
    Med "... y antes de que me diera cuenta, las personas más locas de mi antigua vida llegan llamando a la puerta."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2508
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_64fd587b:

    # Med "Amazing, right?!"
    Med "Increíble, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2511
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_4c6056ac:

    # Z "Interesting turn of events for sure. I didn't know raiders could quit in the first place."
    Z "Un giro interesante de los acontecimientos, sin duda. En primer lugar, no sabía que los raiders podían renunciar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2514
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_847e618e:

    # Med "Yeah, I guess that's the benefit of being a healer. Just about everyone likes you."
    Med "Sí, supongo que ésa es la ventaja de ser una sanadora. Le caes bien a casi todo el mundo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2517
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_0580f849:

    # Z "I guess."
    Z "Supongo que sí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2518
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_c7f3d159:

    # Z "Anyway, Kyra also said that you can help me get an idea about some of the people of interest here."
    Z "De todos modos, Kyra también dijo que puedes ayudarme a hacerme una idea sobre algunas personas de interés aquí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2519
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_e82ad3be:

    # Z "My main concern is that, with the Raiders in control, this place might collapse in a heartbeat."
    Z "Mi principal preocupación es que, con los Asaltantes al mando, este lugar podría derrumbarse en un santiamén."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2520
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_79b203b7:

    # Z "Do you think people will stick around and keep the mines running, if the current... administration, was to be replaced?"
    Z "¿Crees que la gente se quedará y mantendrá las minas en funcionamiento, si la actual... administración, fuera sustituida?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2523
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_d30913f5:

    # Med "I'm a retired raider, I'm not sure if you came to the right place, to be honest."
    Med "Soy una asaltante retirada, no estoy segura de que hayas venido al lugar correcto, para ser sincera."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2524
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_9ceb898c:

    # Med "But I realize that this place will not be the same when Kyra and her gang have their way with it."
    Med "Pero me doy cuenta de que este lugar no será lo mismo cuando Kyra y su banda se salgan con la suya."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2525
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_04b79cff:

    # Med "But now that you say they want to take over it..."
    Med "Pero ahora que dices que quieren dominarlo..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2528
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_6f63e0e5:

    # Med "I do want to keep things going here, to be honest. I don't want to end up having to move away again."
    Med "Para ser sincera, quiero que las cosas sigan su curso aquí. No quiero acabar teniendo que mudarme de nuevo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2531
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_e1c1de85:

    # Z "Then we both benefit from this change of plans, I guess."
    Z "Entonces ambos nos beneficiamos de este cambio de planes, supongo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2532
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_ded5f555:

    # Z "So, let's see... any tips on who I should speak to, around here?"
    Z "Así que, veamos...  ¿Alguna pista sobre con quién debería hablar, por aquí?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2533
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_ca4aa1af:

    # Z "Who can help make it so that the workers won't just leave, in case this place gets overrun?"
    Z "¿Quién puede ayudar a que los trabajadores no se vayan sin más, en caso de que este lugar sea invadido?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2536
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_d3bdd9dd:

    # Med "Well... some will stay, some will leave, and some will attempt to profit from the crisis."
    Med "Bueno... Algunos se quedarán, otros se irán y otros intentarán sacar provecho de la crisis."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2537
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_04327fad:

    # Med "But yes, there are a few people who seem to affect others. You should talk to them."
    Med "Pero sí, hay algunas personas que parecen influir en los demás. Deberías hablar con ellos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2538
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_47b5ea7f:

    # Med "They have a certain amount of leverage. Convince them, and the others might follow their example."
    Med "Tienen cierta ventaja. Convéncelos, y los demás podrían seguir su ejemplo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2541
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_a6cb0afd:

    # Med "Take the guy in the bathtub, maybe you've seen him. They call him Wick."
    Med "Por ejemplo, el tipo de la tina, tal vez lo hayas visto. Le llaman Wick."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2542
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_cf46ba09:

    # Med "He was here before the mines opened and the workers look at him for leadership. He's trying to improve their conditions. He's an actual local..."
    Med "Estaba aquí antes de que se abrieran las minas y los trabajadores le miran como líder. Intenta mejorar sus condiciones. Es un auténtico lugareño..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2543
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_2e421417:

    # Med "...and an abrasive cunt who will speak his mind on anything. Probably can't keep a secret to save his life, but still..."
    Med "... y un cabrón abrasivo que dice lo que piensa sobre cualquier cosa. Probablemente no pueda guardar un secreto para salvar su vida, pero aun así..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2544
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_64f7c299:

    # Med "He knows which way the wind blows, and he's smarter than he sounds."
    Med "Sabe en qué dirección sopla el viento y es más inteligente de lo que parece."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2547
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_3088d1a6:

    # Med "Anyway, if he's planning something, let me know how you intend to deal with it. Maybe I can help smooth things over."
    Med "De todos modos, si él está planeando algo, hazme saber cómo piensas afrontarlo. Tal vez pueda ayudar a suavizar las cosas."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2548
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_82f62c95:

    # Med "The same goes for others like him. The more people stick around, the more likely I will still have a job after all this."
    Med "Lo mismo ocurre con otros como él. Cuanta más gente se quede, más probable será que siga teniendo un trabajo después de todo esto."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2551
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_c32f7a58:

    # Z "You really put him on the spot, there."
    Z "Realmente lo has puesto en un serio aprieto."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2554
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_0d3f029b:

    # Med "I'm just pragmatic. Kyra is a rising leader and the few chumps guarding the walls aren't going to stop her from marching in here."
    Med "Sólo soy pragmático. Kyra es una líder en ascenso y los pocos tontos que custodian las murallas no van a impedir que entre aquí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2557
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_efbc6a3f:

    # Med "I'm an ex-raider, remember? I've been patching up bad guys for years."
    Med "Soy una ex-raider, ¿recuerdas? Llevo años parcheando a los malos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2558
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_95fbaefe:

    # Med "I'm trying to find normal life out here, and if I have to make some tough decisions to do so, I won't say no."
    Med "Estoy intentando encontrar una vida normal aquí, y si tengo que tomar algunas decisiones difíciles para hacerlo, no diré que no."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2561
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_55720ab9:

    # Z "I see. So, I will let you know what I have in mind for these people."
    Z "Ya veo. Así que te haré saber lo que tengo pensado para esta gente."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2562
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_0aef55c9:

    # Z "By the way... why didn't you tell anyone about the attack?"
    Z "Por cierto... ¿por qué no le dijiste a nadie lo del ataque?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2565
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_bbc74bd2:

    # Med "I know Kyra. She has probably been scouting the place for a bit now. Any fleeing or resistance simply means more bloodshed."
    Med "Conozco a Kyra. Probablemente ha estado explorando el lugar desde hace tiempo. Cualquier huida o resistencia sólo significa más derramamiento de sangre."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2568
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_f0d330c8:

    # Med "As for the General and his lapdogs... they can go die in a ditch, as far as I'm concerned."
    Med "En cuanto al General y sus perros falderos... pueden ir a morir a una zanja, por lo que a mí respecta."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2571
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_4535a9a9:

    # Z "Spoken like a true medic. Alright, talk to you later. I will see what I can do."
    Z "Hablas como un verdadero médico. Muy bien, hablamos más tarde. Veré lo que puedo hacer."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2574
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_6bc4810e:

    # "You leave the container."
    "Abandonas el container."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2575
translate spanish settlement_medic_introduction_34e7f4ec:

    # "This Wick guy seems to be one of the people with more relevance. Let's see who else around here is worth my time."
    "El tal Wick parece ser una de las personas con más relevancia. Veamos quién más por aquí merece mi tiempo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2582
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_4ff10533:

    # "An older man sits in front of you, leaning on a red barrel."
    "Un hombre mayor se sienta frente a ti, apoyado en un barril rojo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2583
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_d6c6de3a:

    # "Looking at you with a blank stare, you feel like you can see his wheels slowly turning, trying to identify you."
    "Mirándote con la mirada perdida, sientes que puedes ver sus engranajes girando lentamente, tratando de identificarte."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2584
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_7df87539:

    # "You decide to not judge him by his looks..."
    "Decides no juzgarlo por su aspecto..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2587
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_b6d9660e:

    # OM "Have I seen you before, young man?"
    OM "¿Te he visto antes, joven?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2590
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_02d46938:

    # Z "You would be surprised, old chap; It's my first time here."
    Z "Te sorprendería, viejo amigo; es la primera vez que estoy aquí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2593
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_de17f495:

    # OM "I knew it! I know every face from around here! Welcome to the Overpass."
    OM "¡Lo sabía! ¡Conozco todas las caras de aquí! Bienvenido al Paso Elevado."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2594
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_d50befa2:

    # OM "Will you be working the mines here, like us?"
    OM "¿Trabajarás aquí en las minas como nosotros?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2597
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_0703f599:

    # "His voice sounds hollow, and his tools are tossed around. You were right. He sounds... about as bright as you thought he looked."
    "Su voz suena hueca, y sus herramientas se agitan. Tenías razón. Suena... tan brillante como creías que era."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2598
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_ea17b31d:

    # Z "No, no... I'm not sticking around. I... you know the General, the guy in charge?"
    Z "No, no...  No me voy a quedar. Yo... ¿conoces al General, al que manda?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2599
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_4c077533:

    # Z "I had to talk business with him."
    Z "Tenía que hablar de negocios con él."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2602
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_81cf0b9f:

    # OM "Ah, General, haha. Yes. He is a good man."
    OM "Ah, General, jajaja. Sí. Es un buen hombre."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2605
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2606
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_420961bf:

    # OM "..."
    OM "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2607
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_636de177:

    # Z "And... why is that? He seems... strict in his ways?"
    Z "Y... ¿por qué? Parece... ¿estricto en sus costumbres?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2610
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_ded6c221:

    # OM "The General allows me to work here, to provide for my son, back in the barren lands."
    OM "El General me permite trabajar aquí, para mantener a mi hijo, allá en las tierras estériles."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2613
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_d90fe1f3:

    # OM "I worked hard, so now I can even build a shack right here, as a reward for my efforts!"
    OM "He trabajado mucho, así que ahora puedo incluso construir una choza aquí mismo, como recompensa por mis esfuerzos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2616
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_3c776b7f:

    # Z "The shack behind you? That's yours?"
    Z "¿La choza que hay detrás de ti? ¿Es tuya?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2619
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_7a951b0e:

    # OM "Yes! This is my little home. Usually, workers can't afford to own property."
    OM "¡Sí! Este es mi pequeño hogar. Normalmente, los trabajadores no pueden permitirse tener una propiedad."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2620
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_fc8f4767:

    # OM "But I am very hard working, so the General sold me some land to build my own place!"
    OM "Pero soy muy trabajador, así que el General me vendió un terreno para construir mi propio hogar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2621
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_65cb453f:

    # "Judging from what you see in front of you, the man must be a better miner than he is a carpenter. His construction is shoddy at best."
    "A juzgar por lo que tienes delante, el hombre debe ser mejor minero que carpintero. Su construcción es, en el mejor de los casos, chapucera."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2622
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_b277d4ff:

    # "Then again, he built this on his own, after his shifts in the mines."
    "Además, construyó esto por su cuenta, después de sus turnos en las minas."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2625
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_abdb6d38:

    # "The roof is not complete; the walls are a loose mess as well."
    "El techo no está completo, las paredes también están sueltas."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2626
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_0c99931f:

    # "You wonder how anyone can be proud to call this their home, but you're reminded that resources come at a premium this far from civilisation, and most other workers share communal barracks."
    "Te preguntas cómo puede alguien estar orgulloso de llamar a esto su hogar, pero te recuerdas que los recursos son escasos a estas alturas de la civilización, y la mayoría de los demás trabajadores comparten barracones comunes."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2629
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_40f325fb:

    # OM "I even have my own water storage!"
    OM "¡Incluso tengo mi propio almacén de agua!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2630
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_3830c543:

    # "...he points to the rain barrel in the corner of the room..."
    "... señala el barril de lluvia en la esquina de la habitación..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2631
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_7e105cba:

    # OM "Not many can afford this. I am truly thankful to the General!"
    OM "No muchos pueden permitirse esto. ¡Estoy realmente agradecido al General!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2632
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_42377db7:

    # OM "Many see my home and think: \"I can be there too one day, if I work hard enough!\""
    OM "Muchos ven mi casa y piensan: \"¡Yo también podré llegar a tener una algún día, si me esfuerzo lo suficiente\""

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2633
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_41b95584:

    # Z "They're envious of your shack?"
    Z "¿Tienen envidia de tu choza?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2634
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_3e168052:

    # OM "Yes! They see it and they are reminded that one day they could do the same, if they work hard enough."
    OM "¡Sí! La ven y les recuerda que un día podrán hacer lo mismo, si se esfuerzan lo suficiente."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2635
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_daad5dd4:

    # "The pride in his voice is evident, and you can't deny that his example appears to be a positive force in this settlement."
    "El orgullo en su voz es evidente, y no puedes negar que su ejemplo parece ser una fuerza positiva en este asentamiento."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2638
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_ea6cc69d:

    # OM "It ain't much, but it's honest work."
    OM "No es mucho, pero es un trabajo honrado."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2641
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_1ecac301:

    # Z "I see..."
    Z "Ya veo..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2642
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_d51edf04:

    # Z "You must be someone that many workers look up to..."
    Z "Debes ser alguien a quien muchos trabajadores admiran..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2645
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_51a42886:

    # OM "Yup."
    OM "Síp."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2648
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_5ab3574d_1:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2649
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_420961bf_1:

    # OM "..."
    OM "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2650
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_28e5a76f:

    # Zt "He seems invested in this place more than others. If I can ensure that he survives and sticks around, that will be a good thing for the settlement."
    Zt "Parece que le interesa este lugar más que otros. Si consigo que sobreviva y se quede, será algo bueno para el asentamiento."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2651
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_732767e2:

    # Zt "Maybe I can sow a few seeds in the right directions..."
    Zt "Tal vez pueda sembrar algunas semillas en las direcciones correctas..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2656
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_51f5dbd8:

    # Z "Listen, I was talking to the General as I said."
    Z "Escucha, he estado hablando con el General como te he dicho."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2657
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_c11edb58:

    # Z "And I think that there will be some changes coming up, in the near future."
    Z "Y creo que habrá algunos cambios, en un futuro próximo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2660
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_a83102e3:

    # OM "Changes? What do you mean, young man?"
    OM "¿Cambios? ¿Qué quieres decir, joven?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2663
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_d7f6f659:

    # Z "We discussed helping locals settle permanently. Helping you complete the building of your home could be part of that."
    Z "Hablamos de ayudar a los lugareños a establecerse permanentemente. Ayudarte a completar la construcción de tu casa podría ser parte de eso."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2666
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_e5936be7:

    # OM "Really? That would be wonderful. Thank you so much!"
    OM "¿De verdad? Eso sería maravilloso. ¡Muchas gracias!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2667
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_56e1507b:

    # OM "What is the reason, if I may ask?"
    OM "¿Cuál es el motivo, si se puede saber?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2670
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_42e45812:

    # Z "There is no particular reason, we wanted to honor your commitment and ensure your safety and comfort."
    Z "No hay ninguna razón en particular, queríamos honrar tu compromiso y garantizar tu seguridad y comodidad."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2671
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_67dbfcf5:

    # Z "But as I said, there are going to be a few major changes, before the night is through. It would be best if you didn't stray from your shack for today."
    Z "Pero, como he dicho, va a haber algunos cambios importantes, antes de que acabe la noche. Sería mejor que no te alejaras de tu choza por hoy."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2672
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_233568fd:

    # Z "Tomorrow, I will discuss with the people in charge, and mention your case."
    Z "Mañana hablaré con los responsables y mencionaré tu caso."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2675
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_4dca0898:

    # OM "This I understand. I will do as you say, thank you, young man."
    OM "Esto lo entiendo. Haré lo que dices, gracias, joven."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2676
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_0dad56fe:

    # OM "The General must be very happy that you came here to make things better!"
    OM "¡El General debe estar muy contento de que hayas venido a mejorar las cosas!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2679
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_b9bb5a8c:

    # Z "He is, I'm sure. Very happy."
    Z "Seguro que lo está. Está muy contento."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2680
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_d812c297:

    # Z "Anyway, when the time comes and you are living in a proper home, remember to bring your son here and spread the word."
    Z "De todos modos, cuando llegue el momento y estés viviendo en un hogar adecuado, recuerda traer a tu hijo aquí y correr la voz."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2681
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_775b78a0:

    # Z "This place is going to grow for the better, thanks to people like you!"
    Z "Este lugar va a mejorar, gracias a gente como tú."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2682
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_230bc62e:

    # Z "See you soon, old man."
    Z "Hasta luego, viejo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2685
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_5eeb2345:

    # "You leave..."
    "Te vas..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2686
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_0b567008:

    # Zt "Giving the workers enough motivation to build a future in this place can only be beneficial."
    Zt "Dar a los trabajadores la motivación suficiente para construir un futuro en este lugar sólo puede ser beneficioso."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2691
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_a0e90ffd:

    # Z "Listen... the General and I have been talking."
    Z "Escucha... el General y yo hemos estado hablando."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2692
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_5971f694:

    # Z "And it's about the plans for the future..."
    Z "Y se trata de los planes para el futuro..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2695
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_4edbc822:

    # OM "Okay, what did he say?"
    OM "Vale, ¿qué ha dicho?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2698
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_bbc5005a:

    # Z "You said that you're providing for your son, right?"
    Z "Dijiste que te ocupas de tu hijo, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2699
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_094c03fc:

    # Z "He lives in the barren lands you said?"
    Z "¿Vive en las tierras estériles que has dicho?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2702
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_2057cd3a:

    # Z "Yes, haha. He is a good boy."
    Z "Sí, jaja. Es un buen chico."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2705
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_534d6207:

    # Z "Yeah, so the General and I were drawing plans to allow the workers to reunite with their families."
    Z "Sí, así que el General y yo estábamos elaborando planes para que los trabajadores se reunieran con sus familias."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2706
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_c8fbf8b3:

    # Z "You could build a legacy here, improve your shack, let your son work here too, what do you think?"
    Z "Podrías construir un legado aquí, mejorar tu choza, dejar que tu hijo trabaje también aquí, ¿qué te parece?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2709
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_7ca7ee0d:

    # OM "But... my boy is still young. I don't want him working in the mines."
    OM "Pero... mi hijo aún es joven. No quiero que trabaje en las minas."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2712
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_559811d9:

    # Z "The barren lands aren't much safer, and I bet he still has chores and other things to do."
    Z "Las tierras estériles no son mucho más seguras, y seguro que aún tiene tareas y otras cosas que hacer."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2713
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_d597cc9b:

    # Z "And you living alone here is not smart. You waste money here and also send your son some."
    Z "Y que vivas solo aquí no es inteligente. Desperdicias tu dinero aquí, además del que le mandas a tu hijo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2714
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_5cf8eaa4:

    # Z "So think about it... there are some real changes happening, but my friends will make things better around here."
    Z "Piensa en ello... Habrá algunos cambios reales, pero mis amigos harán que las cosas mejoren por aquí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2717
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_e4e5177c:

    # OM "I see. The changes are good?"
    OM "Ya veo. ¿Los cambios son buenos?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2720
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_68add405:

    # Z "Very good. We will improve life around here, for everybody."
    Z "Muy buenos. Vamos a mejorar la vida de aquí, para todos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2721
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_12d35c8c:

    # Z "Just make sure you stay inside for the rest of today, okay?"
    Z "Asegúrate de que te quedas dentro el resto del día, ¿vale?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2724
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_ed8e3b24:

    # OM "Okay, thank you, young man. You seem like a man with a plan, so..."
    OM "Bien, gracias, joven. Pareces un hombre con un plan, por eso..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2727
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_c1358aa2:

    # Z "I do. Thanks for your time, old man."
    Z "Lo soy. Gracias por tu tiempo, viejo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2730
translate spanish settlement_old_guy_6a4b3a4f:

    # Zt "This guy will believe anything. Pulling his family members here will ensure that he has no reason to leave."
    Zt "Este tipo se creerá cualquier cosa. Trayendo a los miembros de su familia aquí se asegurará de que no tenga ninguna razón para irse."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2737
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_fdf2a1ef:

    # "Before you stands a blonde woman in a pragmatic worker outfit."
    "Ante ti se encuentra una mujer rubia con un atuendo de trabajadora pragmática."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2738
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_eb4d07f4:

    # "She's looking at the water tanks, and after keeping an eye on her, you realise she is in control of at least part of the water supply..."
    "Ella está mirando los depósitos del agua, y después de vigilarla, te das cuenta de que controla al menos una parte del suministro de agua..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2741
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_6af1831e:

    # Z "Hey, I understand you are the person to talk to for some water?"
    Z "Oye, tengo entendido que eres la persona con la que hay que hablar para conseguir agua."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2742
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_4d529a49:

    # Z "I need to fill up the radiator of my car. You know, the pickup."
    Z "Necesito llenar el radiador de mi coche. Ya sabes, la camioneta."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2743
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_4ce96f30:

    # "You point towards your vehicle..."
    "Señalas hacia tu vehículo..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2746
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_023e73b1:

    # Wat "Sorry, man. No water for cars, not from me."
    Wat "Lo siento, tío. No hay agua para los coches, no de mi parte."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2747
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_74be648e:

    # Wat "There's simply not enough of it. We need it for ourselves."
    Wat "Simplemente no hay suficiente. La necesitamos para nosotros."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2750
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_303cb7b6:

    # Z "You're having a water shortage?"
    Z "¿Tienes escasez de agua?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2753
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_950c30bc:

    # Wat "{i}*chuckles*{/i} Did the sun burn your big bald head?"
    Wat "{i}*risilla*{/i} ¿Te ha quemado el sol tu gran cabeza calva?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2754
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_42cdd6ea:

    # Wat "There's desert all around us. And look at what I am working with."
    Wat "Hay desierto a nuestro alrededor. Y mira con lo que estoy trabajando."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2755
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_34eeaa7c:

    # Wat "There's only so much water in the barrels around here, so..."
    Wat "Sólo hay una cantidad de agua en los barriles de aquí, así que..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2758
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_f069c7b8:

    # Wat "Yes, we're low on water. And not just today."
    Wat "Sí, tenemos poca agua. Y no sólo hoy."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2759
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_84f6f144:

    # Wat "Do the math. Only a few wells, some water from the occasional rainfall, but it hasn't rained in a while now."
    Wat "Haz las cuentas. Sólo algunos pozos, algo de agua de las lluvias ocasionales, pero hace tiempo que no llueve."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2760
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_f0ffdc98:

    # Wat "We're down to collecting condensation... in the desert!"
    Wat "Nos dedicamos a recoger la condensación... ¡en el desierto!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2761
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_3aa1e05c:

    # "Looking at the disseminated barrels, you quickly realize that the water reserves are utterly insufficient, compared to the amount of people living here..."
    "Mirando los barriles diseminados, te das cuenta rápidamente de que las reservas de agua son totalmente insuficientes, comparadas con la cantidad de gente que vive aquí..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2762
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_db02bb6c:

    # Z "Is that really all you got? That doesn't seem hardly enough."
    Z "¿Es realmente todo lo que tienes? No parece apenas suficiente."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2763
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_5da90cac:

    # Wat "We have some more collection points spread out across the settlement, but yes, it is... disheartening."
    Wat "Tenemos algunos puntos de recogida más repartidos por el asentamiento, pero sí, es... descorazonador."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2764
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_a253e344:

    # Wat "The General however, in his infinite wisdom, tells me it's good enough and we don't need to invest in better water supplies..."
    Wat "Sin embargo, el General, en su infinita sabiduría, me dice que es suficiente y que no necesitamos invertir en mejores suministros de agua..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2767
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_d07b3726:

    # Wat "We have some reserves, but still..."
    Wat "Tenemos algunas reservas, pero aún así..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2768
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_2a94968c:

    # Wat "While the average guy around here has to go thirsty most of the day, the General and his... buddies... take whatever they want."
    Wat "Mientras que el tipo medio de aquí tiene que pasar sed la mayor parte del día, el General y sus... compañeros... toman lo que quieren."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2769
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_fdfd993b:

    # Wat "There is no real strategy here. If it runs out, it runs out."
    Wat "Aquí no hay una verdadera estrategia. Si se acaba, se acaba."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2770
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_fbe47a0d:

    # Z "Yeah, I've heard that story many times. It's how settlements like this die."
    Z "Sí, he oído esa historia muchas veces. Así es como mueren los asentamientos como éste."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2773
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_3bd89e78:

    # Z "And what about you? Are you going dry all this time?"
    Z "¿Y qué pasa contigo? ¿Te vas a quedar seca todo este tiempo?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2776
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_98f6e60d:

    # Wat "Oh, don't get me wrong. I'm not talking about myself."
    Wat "Oh, no me malinterpretes. No estoy hablando de mí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2777
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_ef056346:

    # Wat "I am the one in charge of the water supply. I keep the pump running, and I get my fair share."
    Wat "Soy la encargada del suministro de agua. Mantengo la bomba en funcionamiento y recibo mi parte justa."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2778
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_87a6fea2:

    # Wat "To be honest, if I didn't get enough to drink, I would've been out of here a long time ago."
    Wat "Para ser sincera, si no hubiera bebido lo suficiente, me habría ido de aquí hace mucho tiempo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2781
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_89c3c779:

    # Z "I see."
    Z "Ya veo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2786
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_d0e6687d:

    # Z "What if I could promise you better tools around here?"
    Z "¿Y si pudiera prometerte mejores herramientas para aquí?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2787
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_bd3c0f2b:

    # Z "If the settlement could provide those, that would help you, right?"
    Z "Si el asentamiento pudiera proporcionártelas, eso te ayudaría, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2790
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_cdfd83ff:

    # Wat "Don't give them any ideas, {i}*chuckles*"
    Wat "No les des ninguna idea, {i}*risilla*."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2793
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_80e527dd:

    # Wat "I mean sure, I would welcome it. But I don't think that the General is up for something like that."
    Wat "Quiero decir que, por supuesto, lo agradecería. Pero no creo que el General esté dispuesto a algo así."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2796
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_8ea99966:

    # Z "Forget the General. Keep this to yourself, but things are going to change around here."
    Z "Olvida al General. Guarda esto para ti, pero las cosas van a cambiar por aquí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2797
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_87dee77a:

    # Z "In fact, for your safety, it's probably best if you stay somewhere safe for the rest of the day."
    Z "De hecho, por tu seguridad, probablemente sea mejor que te quedes en un lugar seguro durante el resto del día."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2800
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_7f7fe87f:

    # Wat "What the hell is going on?"
    Wat "¿Qué demonios está pasando?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2803
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_2112fd5b:

    # Z "Don't worry about that and just think of bigger pumps and better water supplies. I'll see you soon. Stay safe."
    Z "No te preocupes por eso y sólo piensa en bombas más grandes y mejores suministros de agua. Nos veremos pronto. Mantente a salvo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2806
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_dc0caea4:

    # "Promising a few more hydraulic pumps to improve the water situation should win over the settlers, despite the regime change."
    "Prometer unas cuantas bombas hidráulicas más para mejorar la situación del agua debería convencer a los colonos, a pesar del cambio de régimen."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2807
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_39efb9a7:

    # "I should let the Medic know about this encounter."
    "Debería informar a la Médico de este encuentro."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2812
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_c8239b17:

    # Z "Can't you distribute the water to people based on the quality of their work?"
    Z "¿No puedes distribuir el agua en función de la calidad del trabajo?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2815
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_737607d0:

    # Wat "The quality of work? What are you saying, that I should give less to those who are not doing well in the mines?!"
    Wat "¿La calidad del trabajo? ¿Qué estás diciendo, que dé menos a los que no van bien en las minas?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2818
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_ac762178:

    # Z "Yeah, basically that. You said that the General wants all the water for his goons."
    Z "Sí, básicamente eso. Has dicho que el General quiere toda el agua para sus matones."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2819
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_9f7670a3:

    # Z "As, if there's not enough, why do you still give it to those who don't earn it?"
    Z "Entonces, si no hay suficiente, ¿por qué sigues dándoselo a los que no se lo ganan?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2820
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_d466d72e:

    # Z "More water to the diligent means a more productive settlement."
    Z "Más agua para el diligente significa un asentamiento más productivo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2823
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_395fa6c3:

    # Wat "I'm not sure if you're trying to be funny here, or if you're just heartless, because that would be a death sentence to many."
    Wat "No estoy segura de si intentas hacerte el gracioso, o si simplemente no tienes corazón, porque eso sería una sentencia de muerte para muchos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2826
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_124177e9:

    # Wat "But yes, in all seriousness, there are a few workers who are just lazy. I always wondered why they're allowed to stay anyway."
    Wat "Pero sí, hablando en serio, hay algunos trabajadores que son simplemente perezosos. Siempre me he preguntado por qué se les permite quedarse."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2827
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_d2156ab1:

    # Wat "Why do you ask though? I don't think the General would put up with a change like this."
    Wat "¿Por qué lo preguntas? No creo que el General aguante un cambio así."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2828
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_5c7fc1c0:

    # Wat "...You know, people would rise up or something."
    Wat "... ya sabes, la gente se levantaría o algo así."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2831
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_8ea99966_1:

    # Z "Forget the General. Keep this to yourself, but things are going to change around here."
    Z "Olvida al General. Guarda esto para ti, pero las cosas van a cambiar por aquí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2832
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_40bd5843:

    # Z "If you value your safety, and don't care much for the General, I suggest you stay indoors for the rest of the day."
    Z "Si valoras tu seguridad, y no te importa mucho el General, te sugiero que te quedes en casa el resto del día."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2835
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_768c4a5a:

    # Wat "That sounds like something is up, are you planning something?"
    Wat "Eso suena a que algo está pasando, ¿estás planeando algo?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2838
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_df6d1582:

    # Z "Not me, actually, but I promise, things are changing, and you won't have to deal with the General for much longer, and that's a good thing."
    Z "Yo no, en realidad, pero te prometo que las cosas están cambiando y no tendrás que tratar con el General durante mucho más tiempo, y eso será algo bueno."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2839
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_a2cc74f9:

    # Z "Don't worry, you will keep your job. Stay indoors for now and you'll be safe."
    Z "No te preocupes, mantendrás tu trabajo. Quédate en casa por ahora y estarás a salvo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2842
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_7064bc6e:

    # "The water is sparse in this region, so we can't hand it out for free."
    "El agua es escasa en esta región, así que no podemos repartirla gratis."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2843
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_c41edd75:

    # "Especially considering that the raiders will take what they want anyway, even more so than the General's goons."
    "Sobre todo teniendo en cuenta que los asaltantes se llevarán lo que quieran de todos modos, incluso más que los matones del General."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2844
translate spanish settlement_water_woman_299ccbb9:

    # "Taking the water from the less productive settlers will teach the others that either they work hard, or they get out."
    "Tomar el agua de los colonos menos productivos enseñará a los demás que o trabajan duro o se van."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2851
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_8e4051fe:

    # "As you look up, you see a long-haired man sitting under the sun. It's the man that medic pointed out to you."
    "Al levantar la vista, ves a un hombre de pelo largo sentado bajo el sol. Es el hombre que te señaló la Médico."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2854
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_96dedd3c:

    # "Climbing up..."
    "Subes..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2857
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_b960aff6:

    # "...it appears that he is resting in a bathtub cut in half."
    "... parece que está descansando en media bañera de agua."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2858
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_86903cd7:

    # Z "Hey, you. I need to speak with you for a moment."
    Z "Oye, tú. Necesito hablar contigo un momento."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2861
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_545c7d77:

    # Wic "..."
    Wic "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2862
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_79f2967c:

    # "He doesn't seem to react..."
    "No parece reaccionar..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2863
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_07b316c8:

    # Z "Hey, you asleep or something? I'm talking to you."
    Z "Oye, ¿estás dormido o algo así? Te estoy hablando."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2866
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_3702bb52:

    # Wic "Hm..."
    Wic "Hm..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2869
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_a6809480:

    # Z "Good morning. Can we talk for a second?"
    Z "Buenos días. ¿Podemos hablar un momento?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2872
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_f90c8b86:

    # Wic "And who the fuck are you? Can't you see I'm taking a well-deserved nap?"
    Wic "¿Y quién coño eres tú? ¿No ves que me estoy echando una merecida siesta?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2875
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_7823983a:

    # Wic "Wait... you're not even from here. Explains why you can't respect a man's quiet time, after a long day in the mines."
    Wic "Espera... ni siquiera eres de aquí. Eso explica por qué no puedes respetar el merecido descanso de un hombre después de un largo día en las minas."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2876
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_4c959460:

    # Wic "What do you want? Make it quick."
    Wic "¿Qué quieres? Hazlo rápido."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2879
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_c880f9b4:

    # Z "I was told you're someone of influence, and that you're standing up for the worker's conditions..."
    Z "Me han dicho que eres alguien influyente y que defiendes las condiciones de los trabajadores..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2882
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_bdfdc48e:

    # Wic "Pah, fat lot of good am I doing. Have you seen this shithole?"
    Wic "Bah, mucho bien estoy haciendo. ¿Has visto este agujero de mierda?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2883
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_f1cb845a:

    # Wic "But I still don't know you. Why should I tell you shit?!"
    Wic "Pero todavía no te conozco. ¿Por qué iba a decirte una mierda?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2886
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_b5eb531d:

    # Z "My name is [persistent.player_name], I was sent by the Queen of Zeta to take a look at some of the settlements. Yours is one of them."
    Z "Me llamo [persistent.player_name], me envió la Reina de Zeta para echar un vistazo a algunos asentamientos. El tuyo es uno de ellos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2889
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_4c889c4d:

    # Z "Looking at how you... live... around here, it's no wonder you're having trouble."
    Z "Viendo cómo... vives... por aquí, no me extraña que tengas problemas."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2890
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_c798312b:

    # Z "This place is a mess. I would go as far and say that even Zetan slaves live under better conditions than this."
    Z "Este lugar es un desastre. Me atrevería a decir que incluso los esclavos zetanos viven en mejores condiciones que esto."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2893
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_36bdf049:

    # Wic "Yeah... you got that right. We're using fucking tires lately for pillows and to carve some footwear out, can you believe it?"
    Wic "Sí... tienes razón. Últimamente utilizamos los putos neumáticos como almohadas y para tallar el calzado, ¿te lo puedes creer?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2894
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_49dd47a9:

    # Wic "And this goddamn General isn't doing shit about it."
    Wic "Y este maldito General no está haciendo una mierda al respecto."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2895
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_0c57f154:

    # Wic "If it was up to me, we'd take the damn place for ourselves."
    Wic "Si de mí dependiera, tomaríamos el maldito lugar para nosotros."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2896
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_a8a11ac2:

    # Wic "We are the workers, why should we live like shit when they have it good?"
    Wic "Somos los trabajadores, ¿por qué debemos vivir como una mierda cuando ellos lo tienen bien?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2899
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_958cef3c:

    # Wic "So yes, go tell your Queen about this place, but I'm not going to hold my breath for her help, man."
    Wic "Así que sí, ve a hablarle a tu Reina de este lugar, pero no voy a aguantar la respiración por su ayuda."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2900
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_7944d50d:

    # Wic "This place has become a shithole, and me and my boys are only waiting for the right opportunity to..."
    Wic "Este lugar se ha convertido en una mierda, y yo y mis chicos sólo estamos esperando la oportunidad adecuada para..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2903
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_460c20b0:

    # Wic "...anyway, forget what I said."
    Wic "... de todos modos, olvida lo que te he dicho."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2906
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_1cbd97af:

    # Zt "Interesting. He clearly slipped up there. Maybe he really does have something in mind."
    Zt "Interesante. Está claro que ha cometido un desliz. Tal vez realmente tenga algo en mente."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2907
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_ac85ee5e:

    # Zt "If he starts really drawing some support, he might make things difficult to the Raiders, or even cause a mess in the transition."
    Zt "Si empieza a recibir apoyo de verdad, podría dificultar las cosas a los Asaltantes, o incluso causar un lío en la transición."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2908
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_c324cf71:

    # Zt "I need to handle this now."
    Zt "Necesito manejar esto ahora."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2913
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_5efe9cd0:

    # Z "What are your demands actually? I'm sure something can be done."
    Z "¿Cuáles son tus exigencias en realidad? Seguro que se puede hacer algo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2916
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_59428202:

    # Wic "Can was never a problem... the problem is the General and his goons wanting it."
    Wic "El poder nunca fue un problema... el problema es que el General y su matón lo quieren."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2917
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_10a944d7:

    # Wic "We need better tools and protective gear, down in the mines."
    Wic "Necesitamos mejores herramientas y equipo de protección, en las minas."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2918
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_952cfbf5:

    # Wic "The General has the pick of materials when it comes to making fancy armour for himself and his goons, and I have men working buck naked!"
    Wic "El General puede elegir los materiales para fabricar armaduras de lujo para él y sus matones, ¡y yo tengo hombres trabajando desnudos!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2919
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_84dd00e1:

    # Wic "Worse than slaves indeed."
    Wic "Peor que los esclavos, sin duda."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2922
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_322e0831:

    # Wic "Once we got that, we can talk about proper pay. We're barely scraping by here. That ain't right when we're sitting on the biggest coal mine in the region."
    Wic "Una vez conseguido esto, podemos hablar de la paga adecuada. Aquí apenas nos estamos arreglando. Eso no está bien cuando estamos sentados en la mayor mina de carbón de la región."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2925
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_1c70314f:

    # Z "Today might just be your lucky day. The General is on his way out, and if you play your cards right, you might have the pull to get what you ask for."
    Z "Hoy puede ser tu día de suerte. El General está a punto de salir, y si juegas bien tus cartas, puede que tengas el impulso de conseguir lo que pides."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2928
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_bfed97d5:

    # Wic "Whatever you say, man. Let's pretend I believe you..."
    Wic "Lo que tú digas, tío. Finjamos que te creo..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2929
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_f43e337f:

    # Wic "If you don't mind, I need to be alone now. Those long shifts are unbearable without a proper nap."
    Wic "Si no te importa, ahora necesito estar solo. Esos largos turnos son insoportables sin una siesta adecuada."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2932
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_2472586d:

    # Z "Just stay safe for the rest of the day, man... you'll see."
    Z "Sólo mantente a salvo el resto del día, amigo...  Ya lo verás."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2935
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_0abaf87d:

    # "You climb back down..."
    "Vuelves a bajar..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2936
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_824944e2:

    # Zt "If I can't keep this settlement running and trading, the Queen is not going to like it."
    Zt "Si no puedo mantener este asentamiento funcionando y comerciando, a la Reina no le va a gustar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2937
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_23c8968b:

    # Zt "Kyra will be pleased to know she won't have to oversee those workers herself."
    Zt "Kyra se alegrará de saber que no tendrá que supervisar ella misma a esos trabajadores."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2938
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_b3fa8922:

    # Zt "They're willing to keep working as long as they get their fair share."
    Zt "Están dispuestos a seguir trabajando mientras reciban su parte justa."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2943
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_d83e1558:

    # Z "Alright, I will see what I can do about this."
    Z "De acuerdo, veré lo que puedo hacer al respecto."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2946
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_c4bb0d8b:

    # Wic "Excellent!"
    Wic "¡Excelente!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2947
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_cd679f14:

    # Wic "Now leave me be, those long shifts are unbearable without a proper nap."
    Wic "Ahora déjame en paz, esos largos turnos son insoportables sin una siesta adecuada."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2950
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_a6c49ce2:

    # Zt "A fish rots from the head. Getting rid of the worker's leader will give Kyra the upper hand."
    Zt "Un pez se pudre por la cabeza. Deshacerse del líder de los trabajadores dará a Kyra la ventaja."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2951
translate spanish settlement_bathtub_worker_db038c06:

    # Zt "And it will also make the others much more...pliable."
    Zt "Y también hará que los demás sean mucho más... flexibles."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2958
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_13544c2e:

    # C2 "Well hello again, sir."
    C2 "Bueno, hola de nuevo, señor."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2959
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_21580eaf:

    # C2 "You decided to stay after all, hm?"
    C2 "Después de todo, has decidido quedarte."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2962
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_49032146:

    # Z "Yeah, listen... I need to ask you some questions and tell you a secret as well."
    Z "Sí, escucha...  Tengo que hacerte algunas preguntas y contarte también un secreto."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2965
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_63e881eb:

    # C2 "Secret, hmm? You know girls like me love secrets..."
    C2 "¿Secreto? Ya sabes que a las chicas como yo nos encantan los secretos..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2966
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_3498e19c:

    # C2 "What is it about?"
    C2 "¿De qué se trata?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2969
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_4b5dd586:

    # Z "First I need some answers. What do I call you?"
    Z "Primero necesito algunas respuestas. ¿Cómo te llamo?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2970
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_af8af1eb:

    # Z "And are you working in the mines?"
    Z "¿Y trabajas en las minas?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2973
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_7e4790b4:

    # C2 "Okay, sir. What is this all about? {i}*chuckles*"
    C2 "Bien, señor. ¿De qué va todo esto? {i}*risilla*"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2976
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_4fc248de:

    # C2 "You can call me Rue. And no, I was one of the workers... but I ain't anymore."
    C2 "Puedes llamarme Rue. Y no, yo era una de las trabajadoras... pero ya no lo soy."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2979
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_552155b0:

    # Z "So how do you earn your living around here?"
    Z "Entonces, ¿cómo te ganas la vida por aquí?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2982
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_cdba12b1:

    # Rue "Let's say I have... a deal with the General and his buddies..."
    Rue "Digamos que tengo... un trato con el General y sus compañeros..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2983
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_6963c809:

    # Rue "I am too weak to work in the mines, but I have other... talents. I'm not shy to use them either."
    Rue "Soy demasiado débil para trabajar en las minas, pero tengo otros... talentos. Tampoco me da vergüenza utilizarlos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2986
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_76bf5519:

    # Z "I see. I didn't think the miners had any extra income to spare. Why not leave and look for a better place?"
    Z "Ya veo. No creía que los mineros tuvieran ingresos extra de sobra. ¿Por qué no te vas y buscas un lugar mejor?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2989
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_e4a27bfc:

    # Rue "The miners?! Oh, you misunderstood me. I may lend them an ear from time to time, but that's it."
    Rue "¿Los mineros? Me has entendido mal. Puede que les preste atención de vez en cuando, pero eso es todo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2990
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_f6ca2ca5:

    # Rue "As I said, it's the General I have a deal with..."
    Rue "Como te he dicho, es con el General con quien tengo un trato..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2993
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_ffa725f7:

    # Rue "You saw me at the medic's. I'm not doing so hot these days. Bad health and shit."
    Rue "Me viste en el médico. No me va muy bien estos días. Mala salud y demás mierdas."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2994
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_c8070cea:

    # Rue "My brother out in the barren lands is surviving at least in part from what I can send him."
    Rue "Mi hermano, en las tierras estériles, sobrevive al menos en parte con lo que puedo enviarle."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2995
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_22a29775:

    # Rue "I don't know that I would survive moving away now, nor be able to provide for him."
    Rue "No sé si sobreviviría a la mudanza ahora, ni si sería capaz de mantenerle."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:2998
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_c2cd0ae0:

    # Rue "And... honestly, the people around here do look out for me, as best they can. I sometimes feel like something of a mother hen to them. {i}*chuckles*"
    Rue "Y... sinceramente, la gente de aquí me cuida, lo mejor que puede. A veces me siento como una especie de gallina madre para ellos. {i}*risilla*"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3001
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_ea13a220:

    # Z "How familiar are you with the Medic?"
    Z "¿Cómo de familiarizada estás con la Médico?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3004
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_17d91b23:

    # Rue "Yeah, she's a tough one, that one. Not one to cry herself to sleep at night."
    Rue "Sí, ella es una mujer dura. No es de las que lloran por la noche."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3005
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_0156850a:

    # Rue "She's getting jaded, from seeing people die all around her. But for some reason she's taken my case to heart, so I must be doing something right."
    Rue "Se está cansando, de ver morir a la gente a su alrededor. Pero, por alguna razón, se ha tomado en serio mi caso, así que debo estar haciendo algo bien."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3008
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_6086f635:

    # Rue "Now, what about your little secret? Tell me."
    Rue "Ahora, ¿qué pasa con tu pequeño secreto? Dímelo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3011
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_6fcadbc5:

    # Z "Yeah, about that. I talked to the Medic, and I have informed her as well. This settlement is going to change, soon."
    Z "Sí, sobre eso. He hablado con la Médico y también le he informado. Este acuerdo va a cambiar, pronto."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3012
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_4dc63730:

    # Z "Raiders are planning to swoop in and take control."
    Z "Los asaltantes planean abalanzarse y tomar el control."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3015
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_85a827ec:

    # Rue "Why the fuck shouldn't I sound the alarm and give the people a fighting chance?"
    Rue "¿Por qué coño no debería dar la alarma y dar una oportunidad a la gente para luchar?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3018
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_023c7d28:

    # Z "The General and his men don't stand a chance against the Raiders, trust me. The Medic agrees. She knows them."
    Z "El General y sus hombres no tienen ninguna posibilidad contra los Asaltantes, créeme. La Médico está de acuerdo. Ella los conoce."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3019
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_26144b7a:

    # Z "It's going to happen. All I can do is make it go as smooth as possible and save as many lives as I can."
    Z "Va a ocurrir. Lo único que puedo hacer es que salga lo mejor posible y salvar todas las vidas que pueda."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3022
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_6f50413c:

    # Rue "So what's that going to mean for me? I can't work in the mines, and without the General..."
    Rue "¿Y qué va a significar eso para mí? No puedo trabajar en las minas, y sin el General..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3029
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_71b21570:

    # Z "Hm... I have an idea. The Raiders don't know shit about mining or running a community."
    Z "Hm... Tengo una idea. Los asaltantes no saben una mierda de minería ni de dirigir una comunidad."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3030
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_92ecabda:

    # Z "You have experience and know most people around here. I could whisper in the raiders' ear that they need someone to bridge the gap."
    Z "Tienes experiencia y conoces a la mayoría de la gente de aquí. Podría susurrar al oído de los asaltantes que necesitan a alguien que haga de puente."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3033
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_3750f9fc:

    # Rue "To... what now?"
    Rue "Para... ¿ahora qué?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3036
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_cacd3d29:

    # Z "You said people like you around here. You could speak to them for the raiders, and to the raiders for them, work to solve the problems that will inevitably come up."
    Z "Dijiste que a la gente le gustabas por aquí. Podrías hablar con ellos por los asaltantes, y con los asaltantes por ellos, trabajar para resolver los problemas que inevitablemente surgirán."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3037
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_183b316b:

    # Z "Happy workers, stable settlement. It ain't that hard. You could play an important part in that and earn your keep that way."
    Z "Trabajadores felices, asentamiento estable. No es tan difícil. Podrías desempeñar un papel importante en eso, y ganarte el sustento de esa manera."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3040
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_8ea338c0:

    # Rue "I... guess you have a point. I could do that."
    Rue "Yo... supongo que tienes razón. Podría hacerlo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3041
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_0f5b457c:

    # Rue "Thanks, I guess? That's better than sucking off those goons anyway."
    Rue "Gracias, ¿supongo?... De todos modos, es mejor que chupársela a esos matones."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3044
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_5ef6b3bf:

    # Z "These are Raiders we're talking about. They're not exactly a nice bunch either."
    Z "Estamos hablando de los asaltantes. Y no son precisamente un grupo agradable."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3047
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_3dc44540:

    # Z "Anyway... as I said, stay in your camper for now, they will go for the guards and ignore you. Speak to the medic when everything's calming down."
    Z "En fin...  Como te he dicho, quédate en tu caravana por ahora, irán a por los guardias y te ignorarán. Habla con la Médico cuando todo se calme."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3048
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_7ef4a752:

    # Z "See you later, Rue."
    Z "Hasta luego, Rue."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3051
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_f12881d8:

    # Zt "It always helps when people have someone to talk to and it seems she fits the part."
    Zt "Siempre ayuda que la gente tenga alguien con quien hablar y parece que ella encaja en el papel."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3052
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_ef908fa0:

    # Zt "She will certainly help to contain possible unrest in the future."
    Zt "Sin duda, ella ayudará a contener posibles disturbios en el futuro."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3057
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_92cda04d:

    # Z "There's a solution for that, I think."
    Z "Creo que hay una solución para eso."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3058
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_8bcad83f:

    # Z "You're trading sex for crumbs, right now, right? Why not make it official instead?"
    Z "Estás cambiando sexo por migajas, ahora mismo, ¿no? ¿Por qué no lo haces oficial?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3061
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_f404b243:

    # Rue "Are you calling me a whore??"
    Rue "¿Me están llamando puta?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3064
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_3e21f986:

    # Z "Yeah, I guess I am. But I am not wrong, am I?"
    Z "Sí, supongo que sí. Pero no me equivoco, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3065
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_2956aa9e:

    # Z "You're already doing it, why not accept it for what it is, and put yourself under the protection of the Raiders?"
    Z "Ya lo estás haciendo, ¿por qué no lo aceptas como lo que es, y te pones bajo la protección de los Asaltantes?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3066
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_52d2f9d2:

    # Z "I can make it happen that you get the medicines you need, and a fair compensation for your services."
    Z "Puedo hacer que recibas las medicinas que necesitas, y una compensación justa por tus servicios."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3069
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_ac130db9:

    # Rue "I'm not sure about that."
    Rue "No estoy segura de ello."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3072
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_d3bc3175:

    # Z "Take the offer or leave it. I think you're a smart girl. You will make the right choice."
    Z "Acepta la oferta o déjalo. Creo que eres una chica inteligente. Tomarás la decisión correcta."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3073
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_1ff80fab:

    # Z "Either way, keep in mind what I told you; stay indoors for the rest of the day."
    Z "En cualquier caso, ten en cuenta lo que te he dicho: quédate en casa el resto del día."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3074
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_5f465230:

    # Z "I will see you, eventually."
    Z "Te veré, eventualmente."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3077
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_0c003995:

    # Zt "If there is anything that keeps these guys going, it's going to be quality time with a settlement whore. That will keep their motivation high."
    Zt "Si hay algo que hace que estos tipos sigan adelante, será el tiempo de calidad con una puta del asentamiento. Eso mantendrá su motivación alta."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3078
translate spanish settlement_camper_woman_9617feb6:

    # Zt "I don't see how else she can pull her weight around here..."
    Zt "No veo de qué otra manera puede hacer valer su peso por aquí..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3085
translate spanish settlement_simp_2bb0e355:

    # Z "Hey, you. I've seen you before."
    Z "Oye, tú. Te he visto antes."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3088
translate spanish settlement_simp_62832d2b:

    # Vac "M-me? Oh..."
    Vac "¿A.. a mí? Oh..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3091
translate spanish settlement_simp_f1bd2e8c:

    # Z "You were at the General's quarters."
    Z "Estabas en los aposentos del General."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3092
translate spanish settlement_simp_ebbac551:

    # Z "Is it really common for the workers to be so interested in that girl?"
    Z "¿Es realmente habitual que los trabajadores se interesen tanto por esa chica?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3095
translate spanish settlement_simp_cdbf6bab:

    # Vac "Oh, you're talking about Kitty!"
    Vac "Oh, ¡estás hablando de Kitty!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3096
translate spanish settlement_simp_b0b0f02a:

    # Vac "Yeah... she is unique... I am one of her biggest patrons."
    Vac "Sí... ella es única...  Soy uno de sus mayores mecenas."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3099
translate spanish settlement_simp_4fd9bede:

    # Vac "But... why do you ask? There are others like me, but she likes me the most, I'm sure."
    Vac "Pero... ¿por qué lo preguntas? Hay otros como yo, pero el que más le gusta soy yo, estoy seguro."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3102
translate spanish settlement_simp_9efe3479:

    # Z "I see... but how do you know that? Did she tell you?"
    Z "Ya veo... ¿pero cómo lo sabes? ¿Te lo ha dicho ella?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3105
translate spanish settlement_simp_393c00ec:

    # Vac "Kitty does not speak. And the General says we wastelanders don't deserve to hear her voice anyway."
    Vac "Kitty no habla. Y el General dice que los baldíos no merecemos oír su voz de todos modos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3108
translate spanish settlement_simp_97c0ac0f:

    # Vac "But I strongly believe she likes me more than the others, yes."
    Vac "Pero creo firmemente que le gusto más que a los demás, sí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3109
translate spanish settlement_simp_506fc785:

    # Vac "I sadly can't prove it to them, yet..."
    Vac "Lamentablemente no puedo demostrárselo, pero..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3112
translate spanish settlement_simp_900f0148:

    # Z "Hm..."
    Z "Hm..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3113
translate spanish settlement_simp_f41717e3:

    # Zt "Guys like him may not be as relevant as a water supplier, but they sure do look motivated to go into those mines."
    Zt "Puede que los tipos como él no sean tan relevantes como un proveedor de agua, pero seguro que parecen motivados para entrar en esas minas."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3114
translate spanish settlement_simp_5ab30e30:

    # Zt "I might have an easier time swaying him and his friends if I play this smart."
    Zt "Puede que me resulte más fácil convencerle a él y a sus amigos si juego de forma inteligente."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3119
translate spanish settlement_simp_1705fe03:

    # Z "Let's be real though, the reason why you like Kitty is because she looks damn attractive, right?"
    Z "Pero seamos realistas, la razón por la que te gusta Kitty es porque es muy atractiva, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3122
translate spanish settlement_simp_27e774bc:

    # Vac "That's not the reason I like her, man! She's special!"
    Vac "¡Esa no es la razón por la que me gusta, tío! ¡Ella es especial!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3123
translate spanish settlement_simp_e15be9da:

    # Vac "It's about more than her looks..."
    Vac "Se trata de algo más que su aspecto..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3126
translate spanish settlement_simp_be9986b4:

    # Vac "...but yes, I am very attracted to her. I would lie if I said I wasn't..."
    Vac "... pero sí, me siento muy atraído por ella. Mentiría si dijera que no lo estoy..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3129
translate spanish settlement_simp_ef2c4c2f:

    # Z "Do you think that the reason why you're a little... too focused on her, is that perhaps you are just missing a girl in your life?"
    Z "¿Crees que la razón por la que estás un poco... demasiado centrado en ella, es que quizás te falta una chica en tu vida?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3130
translate spanish settlement_simp_bf572916:

    # Z "You know... cuddling, touching, kissing, sex?"
    Z "Ya sabes... ¿abrazos, caricias, besos, sexo?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3133
translate spanish settlement_simp_ed97892a:

    # Vac "..."
    Vac "..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3136
translate spanish settlement_simp_d095b77a:

    # Vac "...I don't know... Kitty makes my days better."
    Vac "... No sé...  Kitty hace que mis días sean mejores."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3139
translate spanish settlement_simp_58f50152:

    # Z "Tell you what... I've been talking to the General. There will be some changes around this place soon."
    Z "Te diré algo... He hablado con el General. Pronto habrá algunos cambios en este lugar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3140
translate spanish settlement_simp_8c497409:

    # Z "What do you say if people like you, who donate so much for Kitty and this settlement, would get one of those Zetan slaves for you to enjoy?"
    Z "¿Qué dices si la gente como tú, que tanto dona por Kitty y este asentamiento, consiguiera una de esas esclavas zetanas para su disfrute?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3143
translate spanish settlement_simp_ac66453c:

    # Vac "You're kidding, right?"
    Vac "Estás bromeando, ¿de verdad?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3144
translate spanish settlement_simp_977a8a2b:

    # Vac "Like for how long, some minutes, an hour? Maybe even two?!"
    Vac "¿Cuánto tiempo, unos minutos, una hora? ¿Tal vez incluso dos?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3147
translate spanish settlement_simp_e201c147:

    # Z "Nope, permanently. You just pay her off, like we do at home. No strings attached."
    Z "No, permanentemente. Sólo tienes que pagarla, como hacemos en casa. Sin ataduras."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3148
translate spanish settlement_simp_7ef7e220:

    # Z "You can let the others know that you'll be the first to get one."
    Z "Puedes avisar a los demás de que serás el primero en conseguirlo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3149
translate spanish settlement_simp_01c9e8cc:

    # Z "Also, if any of your female coworkers need one, let them know that the male slaves are usually cheaper in comparison."
    Z "Además, si alguna de tus compañeras de trabajo necesita uno, hazle saber que los esclavos masculinos suelen ser más baratos en comparación."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3152
translate spanish settlement_simp_2252682b:

    # Vac "Wow, you're the best, man. I don't really know who you are, but if you're saying that you got connections with the General!"
    Vac "Vaya, eres el mejor, tío. ¡No sé realmente quién eres, pero si dices que tienes contactos con el General!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3153
translate spanish settlement_simp_6236af09:

    # Vac "I'm all in!"
    Vac "¡Estoy a favor!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3156
translate spanish settlement_simp_560f07dc:

    # Z "Yeah, as I said, there will be some changes. Stay inside a shack for some time until it's cleared. We don't want you to get hurt. I will speak to you later."
    Z "Sí, como he dicho, habrá algunos cambios. Quédate dentro de una choza durante algún tiempo hasta que se despeje. No queremos que salgas herido. Hablaré contigo más tarde."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3159
translate spanish settlement_simp_5a07089f:

    # Zt "That went well. Giving hard working people like him their own slaves will encourage the rest of the workers to put more effort into their work."
    Zt "Ha salido bien. Dar a personas trabajadoras como él sus propios esclavos animará al resto de los trabajadores a esforzarse más en su trabajo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3160
translate spanish settlement_simp_fcc4ffbf:

    # Zt "After all, happy workers are productive workers."
    Zt "Después de todo, los trabajadores felices son trabajadores productivos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3165
translate spanish settlement_simp_5df6f0c7:

    # Z "Yeah so anyway, you see... about Kitty."
    Z "Sí, así que de todos modos, ya ves... sobre Kitty."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3166
translate spanish settlement_simp_98e2469f:

    # Z "There are changes coming to this settlement, and Kitty in particular..."
    Z "Se avecinan cambios en este asentamiento, y en Kitty en particular..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3169
translate spanish settlement_simp_902b389f:

    # Vac "Changes to... my Kitty?"
    Vac "¿Cambios en... mi Kitty?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3172
translate spanish settlement_simp_9f67bae4:

    # Z "Yeah, so... in short, the General will no longer be in control of her soon, which makes Kitty's position kind of vulnerable, you know."
    Z "Sí, así que... en resumen, el General dejará de controlarla pronto, lo que hace que la posición de Kitty sea algo vulnerable, ya sabes."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3173
translate spanish settlement_simp_918dfad3:

    # Z "It seems people really... I mean, {i}*really*{/i} want to have a go at her. She just looks too good for a bunch of wastelanders not to make use of her."
    Z "Parece que la gente realmente...  Quiero decir, {i}*realmente*{/i} quiere tener una oportunidad con ella. Tiene demasiado buen aspecto como para que un grupo de baldíos no se aproveche de ella."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3176
translate spanish settlement_simp_100f0ab2:

    # Vac "No, my Kitty, they can't do that to her!!"
    Vac "No, mi Kitty, ¡no pueden hacerle eso!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3177
translate spanish settlement_simp_19db17f4:

    # Vac "What will we do? We can't have them spoil her! She's too innocent!"
    Vac "¿Qué vamos a hacer? ¡No podemos dejar que la estropeen! ¡Es demasiado inocente!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3180
translate spanish settlement_simp_ee63afc5:

    # Z "I know, but I found a way to avoid this. You see, Raiders love power more than anything. And power comes at a cost."
    Z "Lo sé, pero he encontrado una forma de evitarlo. Verás, los Raiders aman el poder más que nada. Y el poder tiene un coste."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3181
translate spanish settlement_simp_6bb43f05:

    # Z "A steady flow of wealth should keep them at bay, and Kitty out of harm's way."
    Z "Un flujo constante de riqueza debería mantenerlos a raya, y a Kitty fuera de peligro."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3182
translate spanish settlement_simp_7496d681:

    # Z "If the workers who really care for her promise to keep donating some of their hard-earned coal, the Raiders will turn a blind eye on her!"
    Z "Si los trabajadores que realmente se preocupan por ella prometen seguir donando parte de su carbón ganado con esfuerzo, los Raiders harán la vista gorda."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3185
translate spanish settlement_simp_cf653455:

    # Vac "I will do it. I can even give more than I am already donating, if it really saves her!"
    Vac "Lo haré. Incluso puedo dar más de lo que ya estoy donando, si realmente la salva."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3188
translate spanish settlement_simp_8c947ab7:

    # Z "I know you're doing your best. But yes, we might need more from you and the others. You can tell that we will introduce some kind of... Kitty tax, maybe."
    Z "Sé que estás haciendo todo lo posible. Pero sí, puede que necesitemos más de ti y de los demás. Puedes decir que introduciremos algún tipo de... impuesto sobre Kitty, tal vez."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3189
translate spanish settlement_simp_4b05b8e5:

    # Z "Don't worry, I will promise you to keep her out of their filthy hands, as long as you and your pals keep paying your regular tax."
    Z "No te preocupes, te prometo que la mantendré fuera de sus sucias manos, siempre que tú y tus amigos sigáis pagando los impuestos habituales."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3192
translate spanish settlement_simp_69f30f1b:

    # Vac "Thank you so much. I don't know who you are, but I'm glad you discussed that with the General."
    Vac "Muchas gracias. No sé quién eres, pero me alegro de que lo hayas hablado con el General."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3195
translate spanish settlement_simp_e43d0d10:

    # Z "Don't worry about it. I will speak to you again soon, but for now, it's best you find some shelter somewhere."
    Z "No te preocupes. Volveré a hablar contigo pronto, pero por ahora, es mejor que encuentres algún refugio en algún sitio."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3196
translate spanish settlement_simp_1d190dca:

    # Z "There might be a bit of trouble for some hours, but as long as you stay inside, nothing will happen to you."
    Z "Puede que haya algún problema durante algunas horas, pero mientras te mantengas dentro, no te pasará nada."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3197
translate spanish settlement_simp_07391b0b:

    # Z "Speak you later, [Vac]."
    Z "Hablamos luego, [Vac]."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3200
translate spanish settlement_simp_493d4acc:

    # Zt "These idiots will do everything just to keep that pink haired slut in pristine condition."
    Zt "Estos idiotas harán todo lo posible para mantener a esa zorra de pelo rosa en perfectas condiciones."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3201
translate spanish settlement_simp_a65522bd:

    # Zt "If he tells the others about our plans, we should have a working idiot tax ready to get more gold out of this settlement. Kyra will thank me."
    Zt "Si les cuenta a los demás nuestros planes, deberíamos tener listo un impuesto idiota para sacar más oro de este asentamiento. Kyra me lo agradecerá."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3206
translate spanish settlement_medic_conclusion_35a63e89:

    # Zt "I've talked to everyone that seems to be important."
    Zt "He hablado con todos los que parecen ser importantes."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3207
translate spanish settlement_medic_conclusion_60a7dfcc:

    # Zt "Time to head back to the medic to fill her in."
    Zt "Es hora de volver a la médico para ponerla al corriente."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3210
translate spanish settlement_medic_conclusion_5b36337d:

    # "You head back inside, and you explain to her what happened..."
    "Vuelves a entrar y le explicas lo que ha pasado..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3214
translate spanish settlement_medic_conclusion_d0f7ff1f:

    # Med "Interesting. Looks like you really are trying to fix this place."
    Med "Interesante. Parece que realmente está intentando arreglar este lugar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3216
translate spanish settlement_medic_conclusion_68d84899:

    # Med "I guess you always have some people that draw the short end of the stick."
    Med "Supongo que siempre hay gente que saca el extremo corto del palo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3219
translate spanish settlement_medic_conclusion_8d1ce6c1:

    # Med "Now we only have to make sure that no one dies. Which is why you should not let them wait any longer."
    Med "Ahora sólo tenemos que asegurarnos de que nadie muera. Por eso no debes dejar que esperen más tiempo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3223
translate spanish settlement_medic_conclusion_b0aa560e:

    # Med "Can I be honest? I didn't think it was possible to exploit these people even more, but you convinced me otherwise!"
    Med "¿Puedo ser sincero? No creía que fuera posible explotar aún más a esta gente, ¡pero me has convencido de lo contrario!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3225
translate spanish settlement_medic_conclusion_f91e3618:

    # Med "At least not everyone will feel the exploitation as much."
    Med "Al menos, no todos sentirán tanto la explotación."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3228
translate spanish settlement_medic_conclusion_a2f1f217:

    # Med "Not that I have hard feelings for most of them, so color me impressed."
    Med "No es que les guarde rencor a la mayoría de ellos, así que pónganme al corriente."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3229
translate spanish settlement_medic_conclusion_b97f36b2:

    # Med "You should not let Kyra wait any longer, though."
    Med "Sin embargo, no deberías dejar que Kyra espere más tiempo."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3233
translate spanish settlement_medic_conclusion_2_46da7f3e:

    # Med "I will let the others know what to do once they got this place under control."
    Med "Una vez que tengan este lugar bajo control, avisaré a los demás de lo que deben hacer."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3236
translate spanish settlement_medic_conclusion_2_6ca37ca2:

    # Med "Let the party begin, I guess!"
    Med "¡Que empiece la fiesta, supongo!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3239
translate spanish settlement_medic_conclusion_2_dff04f03:

    # Z "I will be on my way. Thanks for your assistance, Medic."
    Z "Me pondré en camino. Gracias por tu ayuda, Doctora."

