translate spanish d10b143_82717964:

    # Ky "Hey, are you deaf, you idiot?"
    Ky "Oye, ¿estás sorda, idiota?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3283
translate spanish d10b143_2235a1e1:

    # Ky "What are you even listening to, and where did you get those things anyway?!"
    Ky "¿Qué estás escuchando, y de dónde has sacado estas cosas?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3286
translate spanish d10b143_e093b465:

    # As "Hey, I like it... don't be mean."
    As "Oye, me gusta... no seas mala."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3287
translate spanish d10b143_016a1cd7:

    # As "I took them from these tech guys we raided, remember? They were working on one of these..."
    As "Se los quité a los técnicos que asaltamos, ¿recuerdas? Estaban trabajando en uno de esos..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3290
translate spanish d10b143_5f82ee3e:

    # Ky "So do you see any sign of him?"
    Ky "¿Ves alguna señal de él?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3291
translate spanish d10b143_55de02c0:

    # As "Nothing so far, but let me check again..."
    As "Hasta ahora nada, pero déjame comprobarlo de nuevo..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3294
translate spanish d10b143_de07122a:

    # As "Let's see... where were we..."
    As "Veamos... dónde estábamos..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3295
translate spanish d10b143_d9f87160:

    # Ky "Look at his car, I think I see something, no?"
    Ky "Mira su coche, creo que veo algo, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3298
translate spanish d10b143_621480b6:

    # As "Yep! That's the boss! He's giving us a hand signal!"
    As "¡Sí! ¡Ese es el jefe! ¡Nos está haciendo una señal con la mano!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3299
translate spanish d10b143_76299d0d:

    # Ky "Boss? Is that how you call him now?"
    Ky "¿Jefe? ¿Así es como lo llamas ahora?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3301
translate spanish d10b143_588ffa6b:

    # Ky "Why, just because you choked on his dick?"
    Ky "¿Por qué, sólo porque te atragantaste con su polla?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3302
translate spanish d10b143_6e1752ed:

    # As "Now is not the time to get jealous, sister."
    As "Ahora no es el momento de ponerse celosa, hermana."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3304
translate spanish d10b143_43bbb8f3:

    # As "No... I mean... yeah..."
    As "No... quiero decir... sí..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3307
translate spanish d10b143_58780d96:

    # Ky "I really hope he came up with something. If not, we're just going to raze the goddamn place."
    Ky "Espero de verdad que se le ocurra algo. Si no, vamos a arrasar el maldito lugar."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3308
translate spanish d10b143_fae5090b:

    # Ky "I'm not even sure what his plan is. Can you imagine us running a settlement, Asha?"
    Ky "Ni siquiera estoy segura de cuál es su plan. ¿Te imaginas a nosotras dirigiendo un asentamiento, Asha?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3309
translate spanish d10b143_f4b0336f:

    # As "...yeah, I agree. He does look good..."
    As "... sí, estoy de acuerdo. Tiene buena pinta..."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3310
translate spanish d10b143_36eb3cf4:

    # As "Oh, wait! I see the gate opening!"
    As "¡Oh, espera! ¡Veo que se abre la puerta!"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3313
translate spanish d10b143_14007201:

    # As "Looks like he's getting out. That means we're ready to go?"
    As "Parece que va a salir. ¿Eso significa que estamos listas para empezar?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3314
translate spanish d10b143_c4971690:

    # Ky "Yeah, let me tell the others."
    Ky "Sí, deja que se lo cuente a los demás."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3317
translate spanish d10b143_e3a10de4:

    # Ky "Hey, Zion... everything's going as planned. You ready to go?"
    Ky "Oye, Zion... todo va según lo previsto. ¿Estás lista para empezar?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3320
translate spanish d10b143_803cc4da:

    # Zi "Took you long enough! Were we waiting for an official invitation or what?!"
    Zi "¡Has tardado bastante! ¿Esperábamos una invitación oficial o qué?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3323
translate spanish d10b143_7695d53c:

    # Zi "I'm surprised, Kyra. Since when do you take your marching orders from a guy? What's that all about?"
    Zi "Me sorprende, Kyra. ¿Desde cuándo recibes órdenes de mando de un tío? ¿A qué viene eso?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3324
translate spanish d10b143_1e2263df:

    # Ky "I can tell you once this is done. I hope you're excited to bash some heads in because I am."
    Ky "Puedo decírtelo una vez que esto haya terminado. Espero que estés entusiasmada por golpear algunas cabezas porque yo sí lo estoy."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3325
translate spanish d10b143_8987cb53:

    # Zi "You bet your ass I am. Alright, I'll get ready."
    Zi "Puedes apostar tu culo a que sí. De acuerdo, me prepararé."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3328
translate spanish d10b143_99c2866f:

    # Zi "Heard that, Casanova? We're going."
    Zi "¿Has oído eso, Casanova? Nos vamos."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3331
translate spanish d10b143_c55f36cb:

    # Zi "Hey, boyfriend. You hear me?!"
    Zi "Oye, noviete. ¿Me oyes?"

