    Z "... ¿también vas a cumplir tu palabra?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3478
translate spanish d10b_after_attack_131b67a5:

    # Ky "What if I said no...?"
    Ky "¿Y si dijera que no...?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3481
translate spanish d10b_after_attack_2360823a:

    # Z "Then I will have to make you."
    Z "Entonces tendré que obligarte."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3482
translate spanish d10b_after_attack_1dda3429:

    # Ky "I thought so."
    Ky "Eso pensé."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3485
translate spanish d10b_after_attack_05fe46d7:

    # Ky "Why don't you claim your prize, then?"
    Ky "¿Por qué no reclamas tu premio, entonces?"

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3489
translate spanish d10b_after_attack_801bb651:

    # Z "You wouldn't. Not when you're just gagging for it, for me."
    Z "No lo harías. No cuando te mueres de ganas, por mí."

# game/scripts/day10.rpy:3492
translate spanish d10b_after_attack_5b2bab2d:

    # Ky "Look at you... mind-reader..."
    Ky "Mírate... lector de mentes..."

